"実際には<command>svn diff</command>には異なる <emphasis>三種類</emphasis> の"
"使い方があります:"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><sect3><title>
#: en/book/ch02-basic-usage.xml:2124 en/book/ch02-basic-usage.xml:2139
msgid "Examining local changes"
msgstr "ローカルの変更内容の確認"

# uncheck
#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/book/ch02-basic-usage.xml:2128
msgid "Comparing your working copy to the repository"
msgstr "作業コピーとリポジトリーの比較"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><sect3><title>
#: en/book/ch02-basic-usage.xml:2132 en/book/ch02-basic-usage.xml:2197
msgid "Comparing repository revisions"
msgstr "リポジトリーリビジョンの比較"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><sect3><para>
#: en/book/ch02-basic-usage.xml:2141
msgid ""
"As we've seen, invoking <userinput>svn diff</userinput> with no options will "
"compare your working files to the cached <quote>pristine</quote> copies in "
"the <filename>.svn</filename> area:"
msgstr ""
"これまで見てきたように、オプションなしで <command>svn diff</command> を 実行"
"すると、以下のように、作業コピーの内容と<filename>.svn</filename> 領域に"
"キャッシュされている<quote>修正前</quote> のコピー とを比較します。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><sect3><informalexample><screen>
#: en/book/ch02-basic-usage.xml:2148
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"$ svn diff\n"
"Index: rules.txt\n"
"===================================================================\n"
"--- rules.txt\t(revision 3)\n"
"+++ rules.txt\t(working copy)\n"
"@@ -1,4 +1,5 @@\n"
" Be kind to others\n"
" Freedom = Responsibility\n"
" Everything in moderation\n"
"-Chew with your mouth open\n"
"+Chew with your mouth closed\n"
"+Listen when others are speaking\n"
"$\n"
msgstr ""
"$ svn diff\n"
"Index: rules.txt\n"
"===================================================================\n"
"--- rules.txt\t(リビジョン 3)\n"
"+++ rules.txt\t(作業コピー)\n"
"@@ -1,4 +1,5 @@\n"
" Be kind to others\n"
" Freedom = Responsibility\n"
" Everything in moderation\n"
"-Chew with your mouth open\n"
"+Chew with your mouth closed\n"
"+Listen when others are speaking\n"
"$\n"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><sect3><title>
#: en/book/ch02-basic-usage.xml:2168
msgid "Comparing working copy to repository"
msgstr "作業コピーとリポジトリーの比較"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><sect3><para>
#: en/book/ch02-basic-usage.xml:2170
msgid ""
"If a single <option>--revision</option> (<option>-r</option>) number is "
"passed, your working copy is compared to the specified revision in the "
"repository:"
msgstr ""
"<option>--revision</option> (<option>-r</option>) 数値 をひとつ指定すると、リ"
"ポジトリー内の指定したリビジョンと作業コピーを比較します。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><sect3><informalexample><screen>
#: en/book/ch02-basic-usage.xml:2177
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"$ svn diff -r 3 rules.txt\n"
"Index: rules.txt\n"
"===================================================================\n"
"--- rules.txt\t(revision 3)\n"
"+++ rules.txt\t(working copy)\n"
"@@ -1,4 +1,5 @@\n"
" Be kind to others\n"
" Freedom = Responsibility\n"
" Everything in moderation\n"
"-Chew with your mouth open\n"
"+Chew with your mouth closed\n"
"+Listen when others are speaking\n"
"$\n"
msgstr ""
"$ svn diff -r 3 rules.txt\n"
"Index: rules.txt\n"
"===================================================================\n"
"--- rules.txt\t(リビジョン 3)\n"
"+++ rules.txt\t(作業コピー)\n"
"@@ -1,4 +1,5 @@\n"
" Be kind to others\n"
" Freedom = Responsibility\n"
" Everything in moderation\n"
"-Chew with your mouth open\n"
"+Chew with your mouth closed\n"
"+Listen when others are speaking\n"
"$\n"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><sect3><para>
#: en/book/ch02-basic-usage.xml:2199
msgid ""
"If two revision numbers, separated by a colon, are passed via <option>--"
"revision</option> (<option>-r</option>), the two revisions are directly "
"compared:"
msgstr ""
"<option>--revision</option> (<option>-r</option>) でリビジョン番号をふたつ、"
"コロンで区切って指定すると、以下のように、ふたつのリビジョンを直接比較しま"
"す。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><sect3><informalexample><screen>
#: en/book/ch02-basic-usage.xml:2206
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"$ svn diff -r 2:3 rules.txt\n"
"Index: rules.txt\n"
"===================================================================\n"
"--- rules.txt\t(revision 2)\n"
"+++ rules.txt\t(revision 3)\n"
"@@ -1,4 +1,4 @@\n"
" Be kind to others\n"
"-Freedom = Chocolate Ice Cream\n"
"+Freedom = Responsibility\n"
" Everything in moderation\n"
" Chew with your mouth open\n"
"$\n"
msgstr ""
"$ svn diff -r 2:3 rules.txt\n"
"Index: rules.txt\n"
"===================================================================\n"
"--- rules.txt\t(リビジョン 2)\n"
"+++ rules.txt\t(リビジョン 3)\n"
"@@ -1,4 +1,4 @@\n"
" Be kind to others\n"
"-Freedom = Chocolate Ice Cream\n"
"+Freedom = Responsibility\n"
" Everything in moderation\n"
" Chew with your mouth open\n"
"$\n"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><sect3><para>
#: en/book/ch02-basic-usage.xml:2221
msgid ""
"A more convenient way of comparing one revision to the previous revision is "
"to use the <option>--change</option> (<option>-c</option>) option:"
