#: en/book/ch03-advanced-topics.xml:990
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"We should note that, as with other <command>svn</command> subcommands, those "
"related to properties can act on multiple paths at once.  This enables you "
"to modify properties on whole sets of files with a single command.  For "
"example, we could have done the following:"
