# uncheck
#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><para>
#: en/book/ch04-branching-and-merging.xml:432
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Now you and Sally are working on parallel branches of the project: you're "
#| "working on a private branch, and Sally is working on the "
