"provides quite a bit more flexibility in terms of its supported deployment "
"scenarios.  More flexibility means you have to work a little harder to find "
"ways to deploy it incorrectly.  Those reasons&mdash;plus the fact that not "
"using Berkeley DB means there's one fewer component in the system&mdash;"
"largely explain why today almost everyone uses the FSFS backend when "
"creating new repositories."
