"general usage: svnsync SUBCOMMAND DEST_URL  [ARGS &amp; OPTIONS ...]\n"
"Type 'svnsync help &lt;subcommand&gt;' for help on a specific subcommand.\n"
"Type 'svnsync --version' to see the program version and RA modules.\n"
