"$ svnadmin dump /var/svn/repos &gt; repos-dumpfile\n"
"* Dumped revision 0.\n"
"* Dumped revision 1.\n"
"* Dumped revision 2.\n"
"* Dumped revision 3.\n"
"&hellip;\n"
"$\n"
