#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The <literal>[tunnels]</literal> section allows you to define new tunnel "
"schemes for use with <command>svnserve</command> and <literal>svn://</"
"literal> client connections.  For more details, see <xref linkend=\"svn."
"serverconfig.svnserve.sshauth\"/>."
