"exist in a single namespace&mdash;that is, each option is guaranteed to mean "
"the same thing regardless of the subcommand you use it with.  For example, "
"<option>--verbose</option> (<option>-v</option>)  always means "
"<quote>verbose output,</quote> regardless of the subcommand you use it with."
msgstr ""
