"in the user's home directory)."
msgstr ""
"Subversion にデフォルトの場所 (ユーザのホームディレクトリにある<filename>."
"subversion</filename>) ではなく、指定したディレクトリから設定情報を読み出すよ"
"うに指示します。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><term>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:76 en/book/ch09-reference.xml:8719
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:9349
msgid ""
"<option>--config-option</option> <replaceable>FILE</replaceable>:"
"<replaceable>SECTION</replaceable>:<replaceable>OPTION</replaceable>="
"[<replaceable>VALUE</replaceable>]"
msgstr ""
"<option>--config-option</option> <replaceable>FILE</replaceable>:"
"<replaceable>SECTION</replaceable>:<replaceable>OPTION</replaceable>="
"[<replaceable>VALUE</replaceable>]"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:79
msgid ""
"Sets, for the duration of the command, the value of a runtime configuration "
"option.  <replaceable>FILE</replaceable> and <replaceable>SECTION</"
"replaceable> are the runtime configuration file (either <literal>config</"
"literal> or <literal>servers</literal>) and the section thereof, "
"respectively, which contain the option whose value you wish to change.  "
"<replaceable>OPTION</replaceable> is, of course, the option itself, and "
"<replaceable>VALUE</replaceable> the value (if any)  you wish to assign to "
"the option.  For example, to temporarily disable the use of the automatic "
"property setting feature, use <option>--config-option=config:miscellany:"
"enable-auto-props=no</option>.  You can use this option multiple times to "
"change multiple option values simultaneously."
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><term>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:99 en/book/ch09-reference.xml:8753
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:9383
msgid "<option>--no-auth-cache</option>"
msgstr "<option>--no-auth-cache</option>"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:101 en/book/ch09-reference.xml:8755
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:9385
msgid ""
"Prevents caching of authentication information (e.g., username and password) "
"in the Subversion runtime configuration directories."
msgstr ""
"認証情報 (ユーザ名やパスワードなど) を、Subversion 管理ディレクトリにキャッ"
"シュしないよう指示します。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><term>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:108 en/book/ch09-reference.xml:8762
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:9392
msgid "<option>--non-interactive</option>"
msgstr "<option>--non-interactive</option>"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:110
msgid ""
"Disables all interactive prompting.  Some examples of interactive prompting "
"include requests for authentication credentials and conflict resolution "
"decisions.  This is useful if you're running Subversion inside an automated "
"script and it's more appropriate to have Subversion fail than to prompt for "
"more information."
msgstr ""
"すべての対話入力を無効にします。例えば認証情報要求や競合解決などです。これ"
"は、Subversion を自動スクリプト中で実行しており、詳細情報の入力を求めるより、"
"単に失敗したほうが都合がいい場合に役に立ちます。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><term>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:121 en/book/ch09-reference.xml:9404
msgid "<option>--password</option> <replaceable>PASSWD</replaceable>"
msgstr "<option>--password</option> <replaceable>PASSWD</replaceable>"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:124 en/book/ch09-reference.xml:9407
msgid ""
"Specifies the password to use when authenticating against a Subversion "
"server.  If not provided, or if incorrect, Subversion will prompt you for "
"this information as needed."
msgstr ""
"Subversion サーバーに認証するパスワードを指定します。指定しない、もしくは間"
"違った場合は、Subversion は必要に応じて問い合わせます。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><term>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:132 en/book/ch09-reference.xml:8863
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:9433
msgid "<option>--trust-server-cert</option>"
msgstr "<option>--trust-server-cert</option>"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:134
msgid ""
"When used with <option>--non-interactive</option>, instructs Subversion to "
"accept SSL server certificates issued by unknown certificate authorities "
"without first prompting the user.  For security's sake, you should use this "
"option only when the integrity of the remote server and the network path "
"between it and your client is known to be trustworthy."
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><term>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:145 en/book/ch09-reference.xml:9441
msgid "<option>--username</option> <replaceable>NAME</replaceable>"
msgstr "<option>--username</option> <replaceable>NAME</replaceable>"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:148 en/book/ch09-reference.xml:9444
msgid ""
"Specifies the username to use when authenticating against a Subversion "
"server.  If not provided, or if incorrect, Subversion will prompt you for "
"this information as needed."
msgstr ""
"Subversion サーバーに認証するユーザー名を指定します。指定しない、もしくは間"
"違った場合は、Subversion は必要に応じて問い合わせます。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:157
msgid ""
"The rest of the options apply and are accepted by only a subset of the "
"subcommand.  They are as follows:"
msgstr ""
"残りのオプションは、サブコマンドの一部にしか作用しません。以下のものがありま"
"す。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><term>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:163
msgid "<option>--accept</option> <replaceable>ACTION</replaceable>"
msgstr "<option>--accept</option> <replaceable>ACTION</replaceable>"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:166
msgid ""
"Specifies an action for automatic conflict resolution.  Possible actions are "
"<literal>postpone</literal>, <literal>base</literal>, <literal>mine-full</"
"literal>, <literal>theirs-full</literal>, <literal>edit</literal>, and "
"<literal>launch</literal>."
msgstr ""
"自動競合解決用のアクションを指定します。有効なアクションは、"
"<literal>postpone</literal>, <literal>base</literal>, <literal>mine-full</"
"literal>, <literal>theirs-full</literal>, <literal>edit</literal>, "
"<literal>launch</literal> です。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><term>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:175
msgid "<option>--allow-mixed-revisions</option>"
msgstr "<option>--allow-mixed-revisions</option>"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:177
msgid ""
"Disables the verification&mdash;performed by default by <command>svn merge</"
"command> as of Subversion 1.7&mdash;that the items at and under the target "
"directory of a merge operation are at a uniform revision.  While merging "
"into a single-revision working copy target is the recommended best practice, "
"this option may be used to permit merges into mixed-revision working copies "
"as necessary."
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><term>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:189
msgid "<option>--auto-props</option>"
msgstr "<option>--auto-props</option>"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:191
msgid ""
"Enables auto-props, overriding the <literal>enable-auto-props</literal> "
"directive in the <filename>config</filename> file."
msgstr ""
"<filename>config</filename> ファイルにある <literal>enable-auto-props</"
"literal> ディレクティブを上書きして auto-props を有効にします。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><term>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:198
msgid ""
"<option>--change</option> (<option>-c</option>)  <replaceable>ARG</"
"replaceable>"
msgstr ""
"<option>--change</option> (<option>-c</option>)  <replaceable>ARG</"
"replaceable>"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:201
msgid ""
"Used as a means to refer to a specific <quote>change</quote> (a.k.a. a "
"revision).  This option is syntactic sugar for <quote>-r ARG-1:ARG</quote>."
msgstr ""
"特定の<quote>変更点</quote> (つまりリビジョン) を参照するのに使用します。この"
"オプションは、<quote>-r ARG-1:ARG</quote> の簡略記法です。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><term>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:208
msgid "<option>--changelist</option> <replaceable>ARG</replaceable>"
msgstr "<option>--changelist</option> <replaceable>ARG</replaceable>"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:211
msgid ""
"Instructs Subversion to operate only on members of the changelist named "
"<replaceable>ARG</replaceable>.  You can use this option multiple times to "
"specify sets of changelists."
msgstr ""
"<replaceable>ARG</replaceable> という名前の変更リストの内容のみを操作するよ"
"う、Subversion に指示します。変更リストの組を設定するには、このオプションを複"
"数回使用してください。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><term>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:218
msgid "<option>--cl</option> <replaceable>ARG</replaceable>"
msgstr "<option>--cl</option> <replaceable>ARG</replaceable>"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:221
msgid "An alias for the <option>--changelist</option> option."
msgstr "<option>--changelist</option> オプションの別名です。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><term>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:227
msgid "<option>--depth</option> <replaceable>ARG</replaceable>"
msgstr "<option>--depth</option> <replaceable>ARG</replaceable>"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:230
msgid ""
"Instructs Subversion to limit the scope of an operation to a particular tree "
"depth.  <replaceable>ARG</replaceable> is one of <literal>empty</literal> "
"(only the target itself), <literal>files</literal> (the target and any "
"immediate file children thereof), <literal>immediates</literal> (the target "
"and any immediate children thereof), or <literal>infinity</literal> (the "
"target and all of its descendants&mdash;full recursion)."
msgstr ""
"操作の範囲を、ツリーの特定の深度に制限するよう、Subversion に指示します。"
"<replaceable>ARG</replaceable> は、<literal>empty</literal> (指定したターゲッ"
"トのみ)、 <literal>files</literal> (ターゲットとそこにある直接の子ファイル)、"
"<literal>immediates</literal> (ターゲットとそこにある直接の子要素)、"
"<literal>infinity</literal> (ターゲットとすべての子孫、つまり完全再帰) のいず"
"れかになります。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><term>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:244
msgid "<option>--diff</option>"
msgstr "<option>--diff</option>"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:246
msgid ""
"Enables a special output mode for <command>svn log</command> which includes "
"a difference report (a la <command>svn diff</command>) as part of each "
"revision's information."
msgstr ""
"<command>svn log</command> の特殊な出力モードを有効にします。これは各リビジョ"
"ンの情報を、(<command>svn diff</command> のような) 差分レポートします。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><term>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:254
msgid "<option>--diff-cmd</option> <replaceable>CMD</replaceable>"
msgstr "<option>--diff-cmd</option> <replaceable>CMD</replaceable>"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:257
msgid ""
"Specifies an external program to use to show differences between files.  "
"When <command>svn diff</command> is invoked without this option, it uses "
"Subversion's internal diff engine, which provides unified diffs by default.  "
"If you want to use an external diff program, use <option>--diff-cmd</"
"option>.  You can pass options to the diff program with the <option>--"
"extensions</option> (<option>-x</option>)  option (more on that later in "
"this section)."
msgstr ""
"ファイル間の差分を表示するのに使う、外部プログラムを指定します。 このオプショ"
"ンを指定せず <command>svn diff</command> を実行すると、デフォルトでは unifid "
"diff 形式の Subversion 内蔵 diff エンジンを使用します。外部 diff プログラム "
"を利用する場合、<option>--diff-cmd</option> を使用してください。<option>--"
"extensions</option> オプションで diff プログラムを指定することもできます (詳"
"しくはこの章のあとで説明します)。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><term>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:270
msgid "<option>--diff3-cmd</option> <replaceable>CMD</replaceable>"
msgstr "<option>--diff3-cmd</option> <replaceable>CMD</replaceable>"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:273
msgid "Specifies an external program to use to merge files."
msgstr "ファイルをマージするために使う外部プログラムを指定します。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><term>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:278
msgid "<option>--dry-run</option>"
msgstr "<option>--dry-run</option>"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:280
msgid ""
"Goes through all the motions of running a command, but makes no actual "
"changes&mdash;either on disk or in the repository."
msgstr ""
"コマンドの実行をそのままたどりますが、実際の更新は (ディスクやリポジトリー"
"に) しません。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><term>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:287
msgid "<option>--editor-cmd</option> <replaceable>CMD</replaceable>"
msgstr "<option>--editor-cmd</option> <replaceable>CMD</replaceable>"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:290
msgid ""
"Specifies an external program to use to edit a log message or a property "
"value.  See the <literal>editor-cmd</literal> section in <xref linkend=\"svn."
"advanced.confarea.opts.config\"/> for ways to specify a default editor."
msgstr ""
"ログメッセージや属性値を編集するのに使う外部プログラムを指定します。デフォル"
"トエディターを指定する方法は、<xref linkend=\"svn.advanced.confarea.opts."
"config\"/> の <literal>editor-cmd</literal> 節をご覧ください。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><term>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:298
msgid "<option>--encoding</option> <replaceable>ENC</replaceable>"
msgstr "<option>--encoding</option> <replaceable>ENC</replaceable>"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:300
msgid ""
"Tells Subversion that your commit message is encoded in the charset "
"provided.  The default is your operating system's native locale, and you "
"should specify the encoding if your commit message is in any other encoding."
msgstr ""
"指定した文字セットで、コミットメッセージがエンコードされていることを "
"Subversion に伝えます。デフォルトは、あなたのオペレーティングシステムのもとも"
"とのロケールで、コミットメッセージが別の文字セットでエンコードされている場合"
"には、それを指定する必要があります。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><term>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:309
msgid ""
"<option>--extensions</option> (<option>-x</option>)  <replaceable>ARG</"
"replaceable>"
msgstr ""
"<option>--extensions</option> (<option>-x</option>)  <replaceable>ARG</"
"replaceable>"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:312
msgid ""
"Specifies an argument or arguments that Subversion should pass to an "
"external diff command.  This option is valid only when used with the "
"<command>svn diff</command>, <command>svn merge</command>, or <command>svn "
"log --diff</command> commands, where the <option>--diff-cmd</option> option "
"was also used.  If you wish to pass multiple arguments, you must enclose all "
"of them in quotes (e.g., <userinput>svn diff --diff-cmd /usr/bin/diff -x \"-"
"b -E\"</userinput>)."
msgstr ""
"Subversion が外部 diff コマンドに渡す、ひとつ以上の引数を指定します。このオプ"
"ションは、<option>--diff-cmd</option> オプションを指定した、<command>svn "
"diff</command> コマンドや <command>svn merge</command> コマンド、"
"<command>svn log --diff</command> コマンドでのみ有効です。複数の引数を渡す場"
"合、それらすべてをクォートでくくらなくてはなりません (例: <userinput>svn "
"diff --diff-cmd /usr/bin/diff -x \"-b -E\"</userinput>)。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><term>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:329
msgid ""
"<option>--file</option> (<option>-F</option>)  <replaceable>FILENAME</"
"replaceable>"
msgstr ""
"<option>--file</option> (<option>-F</option>)  <replaceable>FILENAME</"
"replaceable>"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:333
msgid ""
"Uses the contents of the named file for the specified subcommand, though "
"different subcommands do different things with this content.  For example, "
"<command>svn commit</command> uses the content as a commit log, whereas "
"<command>svn propset</command> uses it as a property value."
msgstr ""
"そのファイルの内容を、サブコマンドに指定するのに使用しますが、サブコマンドが"
"変われば、その内容の扱いが変わります。例えば、<command>svn commit</command> "
"では内容をコミットログとして扱いますが、<command>svn propset</command> では属"
"性値として扱います。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><term>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:343
msgid "<option>--force</option>"
msgstr "<option>--force</option>"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:345
msgid ""
"Forces a particular command or operation to run.  Subversion will prevent "
"you from performing some operations in normal usage, but you can pass the "
"force option to tell Subversion <quote>I know what I'm doing as well as the "
"possible repercussions of doing it, so let me at 'em.</quote> This option is "
"the programmatic equivalent of doing your own electrical work with the power "
"on&mdash;if you don't know what you're doing, you're likely to get a nasty "
"shock."
msgstr ""
"特定のコマンドや操作の実行を強制します。通常であれば Subversion が拒否するよ"
"うな操作がいくつかありますが、この force オプションを渡し、Subversion に"
"<quote>影響含め何をしようとしているかわかっているから、とにかくやらせてくれ</"
"quote>と伝えられます。このオプションは、電源を入れたまま電子工作をするのに似"
"ています&mdash;何をやろうとしているのかよく理解していないと、きっと嫌な目に遭"
"うでしょう。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><term>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:358
msgid "<option>--force-log</option>"
msgstr "<option>--force-log</option>"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:360
msgid ""
"Forces a suspicious parameter passed to the <option>--message</option> "
"(<option>-m</option>) or <option>--file</option> (<option>-F</option>) "
"option to be accepted as valid.  By default, Subversion will produce an "
"error if parameters to these options look like they might instead be targets "
"of the subcommand.  For example, if you pass a versioned file's path to the "
"<option>--file</option> (<option>-F</option>) option, Subversion will assume "
"you've made a mistake, that the path was instead intended as the target of "
"the operation, and that you simply failed to provide some other&mdash;"
"unversioned&mdash;file as the source of your log message.  To assert your "
"intent and override these types of errors, pass the <option>--force-log</"
"option> option to subcommands that accept log messages."
msgstr ""
"<option>--message</option> (<option>-m</option>) や <option>--file</option> "
"(<option>-F</option>) オプションに渡す、疑わしい引数を正しいものとして強制的"
"に受け入れるように指示します。Subversion はデフォルトでは、サブコマンドの対象"
"ではなく、上記のようなオプションを引数に渡されるとエラーとなります。例えば、"
"<option>--file</option> (<option>-F</option>) オプションにバージョン管理下の"
"ファイルのパスを指定すると、Subversion はあなたが間違ったと見なし、パスを操作"
"の対象とし、ログメッセージの取得先として、他の (バージョン管理外の) ファイル"
"の読み込みに単に失敗します。自分の意図を宣言し、この種のエラーを無視するに"
"は、<option>--force-log</option> オプションを、ログメッセージを受け入れるサブ"
"コマンドに対して指定します。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><term>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:379
msgid "<option>--git</option>"
msgstr "<option>--git</option>"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:381
msgid ""
"Enables a special output mode for <command>svn diff</command> designed for "
"cross-compatibility with the popular Git distributed version control system."
msgstr ""
"名高い Git 分散バージョン管理システムとの、相互互換を取るよう設計された、"
"<command>svn diff</command> の特殊な出力モードを有効にします。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><term>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:388
msgid "<option>--help</option> (<option>-h</option> or <option>-?</option>)"
msgstr ""
"<option>--help</option> (<option>-h</option> または <option>-?</option>)"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:391
msgid ""
"If used with one or more subcommands, shows the built-in help text for "
"each.  If used alone, it displays the general client help text."
msgstr ""
"ひとつ以上のサブコマンドと一緒に使うと、それぞれのサブコマンドの内蔵ヘルプテ"
"キストを表示します。このオプションだけを単独で使うと、共通のクライアントヘル"
"プテキストを表示します。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><term>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:398
msgid "<option>--ignore-ancestry</option>"
msgstr "<option>--ignore-ancestry</option>"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:400
msgid ""
"Tells Subversion to ignore ancestry when calculating differences (rely on "
"path contents alone)."
msgstr ""
"Subversion に対して差分を計算するときに、系統情報を無視するよう指示します (単"
"にパス内容のみを利用します)。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><term>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:406
msgid "<option>--ignore-externals</option>"
msgstr "<option>--ignore-externals</option>"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:408
msgid ""
"Tells Subversion to ignore externals definitions and the external working "
"copies managed by them."
msgstr ""
"Subversion に、外部定義と外部定義によって管理される外部作業コピーを無視するよ"
"うに指示します。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><term>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:414
msgid "<option>--ignore-keywords</option>"
msgstr "<option>--ignore-keywords</option>"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:416
msgid "Disables keyword expansion."
msgstr "キーワード展開を無効にします。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><term>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:421 en/book/ch09-reference.xml:6182
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:9372
msgid "<option>--incremental</option>"
msgstr "<option>--incremental</option>"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:423
msgid "Prints output in a format suitable for concatenation."
msgstr "(他の出力と) 連結しやすい形式で出力します。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><term>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:429
msgid "<option>--internal-diff</option>"
msgstr "<option>--internal-diff</option>"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:431
msgid ""
"Instructs Subversion to use its built-in differencing engine despite any "
"external differencing mechanism that may be specified for use in the user's "
"runtime configuration."
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><term>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:439
msgid "<option>--keep-changelists</option>"
msgstr "<option>--keep-changelists</option>"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:441
msgid "Tells Subversion not to delete changelists after committing."
msgstr "コミット後にも、変更リストを削除しないように Subversion に指示します。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><term>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:446
msgid "<option>--keep-local</option>"
msgstr "<option>--keep-local</option>"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:448
msgid ""
"Keeps the local copy of a file or directory (used with the <command>svn "
"delete</command> command)."
msgstr ""
"ファイル・ディレクトリのローカルコピーを保持します (<command>svn delete</"
"command> コマンドとともに使用します)。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><term>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:454
msgid ""
"<option>--limit</option> (<option>-l</option>)  <replaceable>NUM</"
"replaceable>"
msgstr ""
"<option>--limit</option> (<option>-l</option>)  <replaceable>NUM</"
"replaceable>"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:457
msgid "Shows only the first <replaceable>NUM</replaceable> log messages."
msgstr ""
"最初の <replaceable>NUM</replaceable> 個のログメッセージだけを表示します。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><term>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:463
msgid ""
"<option>--message</option> (<option>-m</option>)  <replaceable>MESSAGE</"
"replaceable>"
msgstr ""
"<option>--message</option> (<option>-m</option>)  <replaceable>MESSAGE</"
"replaceable>"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:467
msgid ""
"Indicates that you will specify either a log message or a lock comment on "
"the command line, following this option.  For example:"
msgstr ""
"コマンドライン上で、このオプションの後にログメッセージやロックコメントを指定"
"します。例えば以下のようになります。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><informalexample><screen>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:473
#, no-wrap
msgid "$ svn commit -m \"They don't make Sunday.\"\n"
msgstr "$ svn commit -m \"They don't make Sunday.\"\n"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><term>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:480
msgid "<option>--new</option> <replaceable>ARG</replaceable>"
msgstr "<option>--new</option> <replaceable>ARG</replaceable>"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:482
msgid ""
"Uses <replaceable>ARG</replaceable> as the newer target (for use with "
"<command>svn diff</command>)."
msgstr ""
"<replaceable>ARG</replaceable> を新しいほうのターゲットとして使用します "
"(<command>svn diff</command> とともに使います)。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><term>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:488
msgid "<option>--no-auto-props</option>"
msgstr "<option>--no-auto-props</option>"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:490
msgid ""
"Disables auto-props, overriding the <literal>enable-auto-props</literal> "
"directive in the <filename>config</filename> file."
msgstr ""
"<filename>config</filename> ファイル中の <literal>enable-auto-props</"
"literal> ディレクティブを上書きする形で auto-props を無効にします。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><term>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:497 en/book/ch09-reference.xml:7549
msgid "<option>--no-diff-deleted</option>"
msgstr "<option>--no-diff-deleted</option>"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:499
msgid ""
"Prevents Subversion from printing differences for deleted files.  The "
"default behavior when you remove a file is for <command>svn diff</command> "
"to print the same differences that you would see if you had left the file "
"but removed all the content."
msgstr ""
"削除されたファイルの差分を出力しないよう Subversion に指示します。ファイルを"
"削除した際の <command>svn diff</command> のデフォルト動作は、ファイルが残って"
"いて内容をすべて削除した場合の差分と、同じ出力になります。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><term>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:508
msgid "<option>--no-ignore</option>"
msgstr "<option>--no-ignore</option>"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:510
msgid ""
"Shows files in the status listing that would normally be omitted since they "
"match a pattern in the <literal>global-ignores</literal> configuration "
"option or the <literal>svn:ignore</literal> property.  See <xref linkend="
"\"svn.advanced.confarea.opts.config\"/> and <xref linkend=\"svn.advanced."
"props.special.ignore\"/> for more information."
msgstr ""
"<literal>global-ignores</literal> 設定オプションや、<literal>svn:ignore</"
"literal> 属性にマッチしたため、通常なら省略されるようなファイルのステータス一"
"覧を表示します。詳しい情報は、<xref linkend=\"svn.advanced.confarea.opts."
"config\"/> や <xref linkend=\"svn.advanced.props.special.ignore\"/> をご覧く"
"ださい。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><term>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:521
msgid "<option>--no-unlock</option>"
msgstr "<option>--no-unlock</option>"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:523
msgid ""
"Tells Subversion not to automatically unlock files (the default commit "
"behavior is to unlock all files listed as part of the commit).  See <xref "
"linkend=\"svn.advanced.locking\"/> for more information."
msgstr ""
"自動的にファイルをロック解除しないよう Subversion に指示します (デフォルトの"
"コミットの動作は、コミットの一部として対象ファイルをすべてロック解除します)。"
"詳しい情報は、<xref linkend=\"svn.advanced.locking\"/> をご覧ください。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><term>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:531
msgid "<option>--non-recursive</option> (<option>-N</option>)"
msgstr "<option>--non-recursive</option> (<option>-N</option>)"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:533
msgid ""
"<emphasis>Deprecated</emphasis>.  Stops a subcommand from recursing into "
"subdirectories.  Most subcommands recurse by default, but some do not.  "
"Users should avoid this option and use the more precise <option>--depth</"
"option> option instead.  For most subcommands, specifying <option>--non-"
"recursive</option> produces behavior which is the same as if you'd specified "
"<option>--depth=files</option>, but there are exceptions: non-recursive "
"<command>svn status</command> operates at the <literal>immediates</literal> "
"depth, and the non-recursive forms of <command>svn revert</command>, "
"<command>svn add</command>, and <command>svn commit</command> operate at an "
"<literal>empty</literal> depth."
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><term>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:550
msgid "<option>--notice-ancestry</option>"
msgstr "<option>--notice-ancestry</option>"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:552
msgid "Pays attention to ancestry when calculating differences."
msgstr "差分を計算するときに系統情報を考慮します。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><term>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:558
msgid "<option>--old</option> <replaceable>ARG</replaceable>"
msgstr "<option>--old</option> <replaceable>ARG</replaceable>"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:560
msgid ""
"Uses <replaceable>ARG</replaceable> as the older target (for use with "
"<command>svn diff</command>)."
msgstr ""
"<replaceable>ARG</replaceable> を古いほうのターゲットとして使用します "
"(<command>svn diff</command> とともに使います)。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><term>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:566
msgid "<option>--parents</option>"
msgstr "<option>--parents</option>"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:568
msgid ""
"Creates and adds nonexistent or nonversioned parent subdirectories to the "
"working copy or repository as part of an operation.  This is useful for "
"automatically creating multiple subdirectories where none currently exist.  "
"If performed on a URL, all the directories will be created in a single "
"commit."
msgstr ""
"操作の一部として、作業コピーやリポジトリーに存在しない、ないしバージョン管理"
"下にない親のサブディレクトリを、作成・追加します。まだ存在しない複数のサブ"
"ディレクトリを、自動的に作成するのに便利です。URL を指定した場合、作成した"
"ディレクトリは一度にコミットされます。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><refentry><refsect1><variablelist><varlistentry><term>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:578 en/book/ch09-reference.xml:6237
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:8774 en/book/ch09-reference.xml:9415
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:10361
msgid "<option>--quiet</option> (<option>-q</option>)"
msgstr "<option>--quiet</option> (<option>-q</option>)"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:580 en/book/ch09-reference.xml:8776
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:9417
msgid ""
"Requests that the client print only essential information while performing "
"an operation."
msgstr "実行中に重要な情報だけを出力するように指示します。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><term>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:586
msgid "<option>--record-only</option>"
msgstr "<option>--record-only</option>"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:588
msgid ""
"Marks revisions as merged, for use with <option>--revision</option> "
"(<option>-r</option>)."
msgstr ""
"<option>--revision</option> (<option>-r</option>) と一緒に使用し、マージされ"
"たとリビジョンにマークします。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><term>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:595
msgid "<option>--recursive</option> (<option>-R</option>)"
msgstr "<option>--recursive</option> (<option>-R</option>)"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:597
msgid ""
"Makes a subcommand recurse into subdirectories.  Most subcommands recurse by "
"default."
msgstr ""
"サブコマンドをサブディレクトリに対して再帰的に実行するようにします。ほとんど"
"のサブコマンドはデフォルトで再帰的です。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><term>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:603
msgid "<option>--reintegrate</option>"
msgstr "<option>--reintegrate</option>"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:605
msgid ""
"Used with the <command>svn merge</command> subcommand, merges all of the "
"source URL's changes into the working copy.  See <xref linkend=\"svn."
"branchemerge.basicmerging.stayinsync\"/> for details."
msgstr ""
"<command>svn merge</command> サブコマンドと一緒に使用し、マージ元 URL の変更"
"をすべて作業コピーにマージします。詳細は <xref linkend=\"svn.branchemerge."
"basicmerging.stayinsync\"/> をご覧ください。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><term>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:614
msgid ""
"<option>--relocate</option> <replaceable>FROM TO [PATH...]</replaceable>"
msgstr ""
"<option>--relocate</option> <replaceable>FROM TO [PATH...]</replaceable>"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:617
msgid ""
"Deprecated.  When used with the <command>svn switch</command> subcommand, "
"changes the location of the repository that your working copy references.  "
"The preferred approach as of Subversion 1.7, however, is to use the "
"<command>svn relocate</command> subcommand.  See <xref linkend=\"svn.ref.svn."
"c.relocate\" /> for more details and an example."
msgstr ""
"非推奨です。<command>svn switch</command> サブコマンドと一緒に使うと、作業コ"
"ピーが参照しているリポジトリーの場所を変更します。しかし、Subversion 1.7 で"
"は、<command>svn relocate</command> サブコマンドの使用をおすすめします。詳細"
"やサンプルについては <xref linkend=\"svn.ref.svn.c.relocate\" /> をご覧くださ"
"い。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><term>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:628
msgid "<option>--remove</option> <replaceable>ARG</replaceable>"
msgstr "<option>--remove</option> <replaceable>ARG</replaceable>"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:631
msgid "Disassociates <replaceable>ARG</replaceable> from a changelist"
msgstr "changelist から、<replaceable>ARG</replaceable> を切り離します。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><term>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:637
msgid ""
"<option>--revision</option> (<option>-r</option>)  <replaceable>REV</"
"replaceable>"
msgstr ""
"<option>--revision</option> (<option>-r</option>)  <replaceable>REV</"
"replaceable>"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:641
msgid ""
"Indicates that you're going to supply a revision (or range of revisions) for "
"a particular operation.  You can provide revision numbers, keywords, or "
"dates (in curly braces) as arguments to the revision option.  If you wish to "
"offer a range of revisions, you can provide two revisions separated by a "
"colon.  For example:"
msgstr ""
"特定の操作で、リビジョン (またはリビジョン範囲) を指定します。revision オプ"
"ションの引数として、リビジョン番号、キーワード、日付 (中かっこ内) を指定でき"
"ます。リビジョン範囲を指定する場合、二つのリビジョンをコロンで区切ってくださ"
"い。以下に例を示します。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><informalexample><screen>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:651
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"$ svn log -r 1729\n"
"$ svn log -r 1729:HEAD\n"
"$ svn log -r 1729:1744\n"
"$ svn log -r {2001-12-04}:{2002-02-17}\n"
"$ svn log -r 1729:{2002-02-17}\n"
msgstr ""
"$ svn log -r 1729\n"
"$ svn log -r 1729:HEAD\n"
"$ svn log -r 1729:1744\n"
"$ svn log -r {2001-12-04}:{2002-02-17}\n"
"$ svn log -r 1729:{2002-02-17}\n"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:659
msgid "See <xref linkend=\"svn.tour.revs.keywords\"/> for more information."
msgstr "詳しくは <xref linkend=\"svn.tour.revs.keywords\"/> をご覧ください。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><term>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:665 en/book/ch09-reference.xml:7580
msgid "<option>--revprop</option>"
msgstr "<option>--revprop</option>"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:667 en/book/ch09-reference.xml:7582
msgid ""
"Operates on a revision property instead of a property specific to a file or "
"directory.  This option requires that you also pass a revision with the "
"<option>--revision</option> (<option>-r</option>)  option."
msgstr ""
"指定したファイルやディレクトリの属性のかわりに、リビジョンの属性を操作しま"
"す。このオプションを使う場合、<option>--revision</option> (<option>-r</"
"option>) オプションを使ってリビジョンも渡す必要があります。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><term>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:676
msgid "<option>--set-depth</option> <replaceable>ARG</replaceable>"
msgstr "<option>--set-depth</option> <replaceable>ARG</replaceable>"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:679
msgid ""
"Sets the sticky depth on a directory in a working copy to one of "
"<literal>exclude</literal>, <literal>empty</literal>, <literal>files</"
"literal>, <literal>immediates</literal>, or <literal>infinity</literal>.  "
"For detailed coverage of what these mean and how to use this option, see "
"<xref linkend=\"svn.advanced.sparsedirs\" />."
msgstr ""
"作業コピーのディレクトリに、<literal>exclude</literal>, <literal>empty</"
"literal>, <literal>files</literal>, <literal>immediates</literal>, "
"<literal>infinity</literal> のいずれかの深さを設定します。これらの意味やこの"
"オプションの使用法の詳細は、<xref linkend=\"svn.advanced.sparsedirs\" /> をご"
"覧ください。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><term>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:689
msgid "<option>--show-copies-as-adds</option>"
msgstr "<option>--show-copies-as-adds</option>"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:691
msgid ""
"Enables a special output mode for <command>svn diff</command> in which the "
"content difference for a file created via a copy operation appears as it "
"would for a brand new file (with each line therein appearing as an addition "
"to an empty file) rather than as a delta against the original file from "
"which the copy was created."
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><term>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:702
msgid "<option>--show-revs</option> <replaceable>ARG</replaceable>"
msgstr "<option>--show-revs</option> <replaceable>ARG</replaceable>"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:704
msgid ""
"Used to make <command>svn mergeinfo</command> display either "
"<literal>merged</literal> or <literal>eligible</literal> revisions."
msgstr ""
"<command>svn mergeinfo</command> に、<literal>merged</literal> リビジョンか "
"<literal>eligible</literal> リビジョンを表示させるのに使用します。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><term>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:711
msgid "<option>--show-updates</option> (<option>-u</option>)"
msgstr "<option>--show-updates</option> (<option>-u</option>)"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:713
msgid ""
"Causes the client to display information about which files in your working "
"copy are out of date.  This doesn't actually update any of your files&mdash;"
"it just shows you which files will be updated if you then use <command>svn "
"update</command>."
msgstr ""
"作業コピーのどのファイルが古くなっているかといった情報をクライアントに表示し"
"ます。これは実際にはファイルを更新しません&mdash;<command>svn update</"
"command> を実行した場合に、どのファイルが更新されるかを表示するだけです。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><term>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:723
msgid "<option>--stop-on-copy</option>"
msgstr "<option>--stop-on-copy</option>"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:725
msgid ""
"Causes a Subversion subcommand that traverses the history of a versioned "
"resource to stop harvesting that historical information when a copy&mdash;"
"that is, a location in history where that resource was copied from another "
"location in the repository&mdash;is encountered."
msgstr ""
"バージョン管理下リソースの履歴を巡回する Subversion のサブコマンドに対して、"
"コピー (履歴中でリポジトリーのほかの場所からコピーされたリソースがある場所) "
"検出時に履歴情報の収集を中止させます。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><term>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:735
msgid "<option>--strict</option>"
msgstr "<option>--strict</option>"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:737
msgid ""
"Causes Subversion to use strict semantics, a notion that is rather vague "
"unless talking about specific subcommands (namely, <command>svn propget</"
"command>)."
msgstr ""
"Subversion が厳密なセマンティックスを使うようにします。このセマンティックスと"
"は、具体的なサブコマンド (はっきり言うと <command>svn propget</command>) につ"
"いて説明しないと、漠然とした概念になってしまいます。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><term>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:744 en/book/ch09-reference.xml:9993
msgid "<option>--targets</option> <replaceable>FILENAME</replaceable>"
msgstr "<option>--targets</option> <replaceable>FILENAME</replaceable>"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:747
msgid ""
"Tells Subversion to read additional target paths for the operation from "
"<replaceable>FILENAME</replaceable>.  <replaceable>FILENAME</replaceable> "
"should contain one path per line, with each path expected to use the same "
"encoding and formatting that it would if you had specified it directly as an "
"argument on the command line."
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><term>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:758
msgid "<option>--use-merge-history</option> (<option>-g</option>)"
msgstr "<option>--use-merge-history</option> (<option>-g</option>)"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:761
msgid "Uses or displays additional information from merge history."
msgstr "マージ履歴から追加情報を表示するのに使用します。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><term>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:767
msgid "<option>--verbose</option> (<option>-v</option>)"
msgstr "<option>--verbose</option> (<option>-v</option>)"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:769
msgid ""
"Requests that the client print out as much information as it can while "
"running any subcommand.  This may result in Subversion printing out "
"additional fields, detailed information about every file, or additional "
"information regarding its actions."
msgstr ""
"サブコマンド実行時に、できるだけ多くの情報を出力するように、クライアントに指"
"示します。Subversion は、追加フィールドや、すべてのファイルの詳細情報、動作内"
"容についての追加情報などを出力するようになります。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><refentry><refsect1><variablelist><varlistentry><term>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:778 en/book/ch09-reference.xml:9905
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:10369
msgid "<option>--version</option>"
msgstr "<option>--version</option>"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:780
msgid ""
"Prints the client version info.  This information includes not only the "
"version number of the client, but also a listing of all repository access "
"modules that the client can use to access a Subversion repository.  With "
"<option>--quiet</option> (<option>-q</option>) it prints only the version "
"number in a compact form."
msgstr ""
"クライアントのバージョン情報を出力します。この情報は、クライアントのバージョ"
"ン番号だけでなく、クライアントが Subversion リポジトリーにアクセスする際の、"
"リポジトリーアクセスモジュールのすべてを一覧で出力します。<option>--quiet</"
"option> (<option>-q</option>) と一緒に指定すると、短い形式でバージョン番号を"
"出力します。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><term>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:790
msgid "<option>--with-all-revprops</option>"
msgstr "<option>--with-all-revprops</option>"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:792
msgid ""
"Used with the <option>--xml</option> option to <command>svn log</command>, "
"instructs Subversion to retrieve and display all revision properties&mdash;"
"the standard ones used internally by Subversion as well as any user-defined "
"ones&mdash;in the log output."
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><term>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:801
msgid "<option>--with-no-revprops</option>"
msgstr "<option>--with-no-revprops</option>"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:803
msgid ""
"Used with the <option>--xml</option> option to <command>svn log</command>, "
"instructs Subversion to omit all revision properties&mdash;including the "
"standard log message, author, and revision datestamp&mdash;from the log "
"output."
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><term>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:812
msgid "<option>--with-revprop</option> <replaceable>ARG</replaceable>"
msgstr "<option>--with-revprop</option> <replaceable>ARG</replaceable>"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:815
msgid ""
"When used with any command that writes to the repository, sets the revision "
"property, using the <replaceable>NAME=VALUE</replaceable> format, "
"<replaceable>NAME</replaceable> to <replaceable>VALUE</replaceable>.  When "
"used with <command>svn log</command> in <option>--xml</option> mode, this "
"displays the value of <replaceable>ARG</replaceable> in the log output."
msgstr ""
"リポジトリーに書き込むコマンドで使用すると、リビジョン属性をセットします。"
"<replaceable>NAME=VALUE</replaceable> という形式を用い、<replaceable>NAME</"
"replaceable> に <replaceable>VALUE</replaceable> をセットします。"
"<command>svn log</command> の <option>--xml</option> モードで使用すると、ログ"
"出力に<replaceable>ARG</replaceable> の値を表示します。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><term>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:826
msgid "<option>--xml</option>"
msgstr "<option>--xml</option>"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:828
msgid "Prints output in XML format."
msgstr "XML フォーマットで出力します。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><title>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:838
msgid "svn Subcommands"
msgstr "svn のサブコマンド"

