"A         foo.c\n"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refsect1><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:904
msgid ""
"When adding a directory, the default behavior of <command>svn add</command> "
"is to recurse:"
msgstr ""
"ディレクトリを追加する際、<command>svn add</command> のデフォルト動作は再帰的"
"です。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refsect1><informalexample><screen>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:909
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"$ svn add testdir\n"
"A         testdir\n"
"A         testdir/a\n"
"A         testdir/b\n"
"A         testdir/c\n"
"A         testdir/d\n"
msgstr ""
"$ svn add testdir\n"
"A         testdir\n"
"A         testdir/a\n"
"A         testdir/b\n"
"A         testdir/c\n"
"A         testdir/d\n"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refsect1><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:918
msgid "You can add a directory without adding its contents:"
msgstr ""
"内部にあるファイルを追加せずに、ディレクトリのみを追加することができます。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refsect1><informalexample><screen>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:923
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"$ svn add --depth=empty otherdir\n"
"A         otherdir\n"
msgstr ""
"$ svn add --depth=empty otherdir\n"
"A         otherdir\n"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refsect1><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:928
msgid ""
"Normally, the command <userinput>svn add *</userinput> will skip over any "
"directories that are already under version control.  Sometimes, however, you "
"may want to add every unversioned object in your working copy, including "
"those hiding deeper.  Passing the <option>--force</option> option makes "
"<command>svn add</command> recurse into versioned directories:"
msgstr ""
"通常、コマンド <userinput>svn add *</userinput> はすでにバージョン管理下にあ"
"るすべてのディレクトリをスキップします。しかし作業コピーにある、バージョン管"
"理下にないオブジェクトをすべて、深いところに隠れているものも含め、再帰的に追"
"加したいこともあるでしょう。<option>--force</option> オプションを渡すと、既に"
"バージョン管理されているディレクトリにも、再帰的に <command>svn add</"
"command> を行います。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refsect1><informalexample><screen>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:939
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"$ svn add * --force\n"
"A         foo.c\n"
"A         somedir/bar.c\n"
"A  (bin)  otherdir/docs/baz.doc\n"
"&hellip;\n"
msgstr ""
"$ svn add * --force\n"
"A         foo.c\n"
"A         somedir/bar.c\n"
"A  (bin)  otherdir/docs/baz.doc\n"
"&hellip;\n"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><indexterm><tertiary>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:956
msgid "blame"
msgstr "blame"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refnamediv><refname>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:960
msgid "svn blame (praise, annotate, ann)"
msgstr "svn blame (praise, annotate, ann)"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refnamediv><refpurpose>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:961
msgid ""
"Show author and revision information inline for the specified files or URLs."
msgstr ""
"指定したファイルや URL の変更者とリビジョン情報を、インラインで表示 します。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refsect1><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:966
msgid "<literal>svn blame TARGET[@REV]...</literal>"
msgstr "<literal>svn blame TARGET[@REV]...</literal>"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refsect1><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:971
msgid ""
"Show author and revision information inline for the specified files or "
"URLs.  Each line of text is annotated at the beginning with the author "
"(username) and the revision number for the last change to that line."
msgstr ""
"指定したファイルや URL の変更者とリビジョン情報をインラインで表示します。テキ"
"ストの各行には先頭に変更者 (ユーザー名) と、その行に最後に変更があったリビ"
"ジョン番号の注釈がつきます。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refsect1><informalexample><screen>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:982
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"--extensions (-x) ARG\n"
"--force\n"
"--incremental\n"
"--revision (-r) REV\n"
"--use-merge-history (-g)\n"
"--verbose (-v)\n"
"--xml\n"
msgstr ""
"--extensions (-x) ARG\n"
"--force\n"
"--incremental\n"
"--revision (-r) REV\n"
"--use-merge-history (-g)\n"
"--verbose (-v)\n"
"--xml\n"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refsect1><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:1018
msgid ""
"If you want to see blame-annotated source for <filename>readme.txt</"
"filename> in your test repository:"
msgstr ""
"自分の test リポジトリーにある <filename>readme.txt</filename> の注釈付きソー"
"スを見る場合、以下のようにしてください。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refsect1><informalexample><screen>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:1024
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"$ svn blame http://svn.red-bean.com/repos/test/readme.txt\n"
"     3      sally This is a README file.\n"
"     5      harry You should read this.\n"
msgstr ""
"$ svn blame http://svn.red-bean.com/repos/test/readme.txt\n"
"     3      sally This is a README file.\n"
"     5      harry You should read this.\n"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refsect1><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:1030
msgid ""
"Even if <command>svn blame</command> says that Harry last modified "
"<filename>readme.txt</filename> in revision 5, you'll have to examine "
"exactly what the revision changed to be sure that Harry changed the "
"<emphasis>context</emphasis> of the line&mdash;he may have adjusted just the "
"whitespace."
msgstr ""
"リビジョン 5 で <filename>readme.txt</filename> を最後に更新したのが Harry だ"
"と <command>svn blame</command> が言ったとしても、そのリビジョンで、Harry が"
"行の <emphasis>文脈</emphasis> を変更したとはっきり言えるかどうか、調べなくて"
"はならないでしょう &mdash; 空白の調整をしただけかもしれません。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refsect1><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:1038
msgid ""
"If you use the <option>--xml</option> option, you can get XML output "
"describing the blame annotations, but not the contents of the lines "
"themselves:"
msgstr ""
"<option>--xml</option> オプションを使用すると、担当注釈の XML 出力を得られま"
"す。しかしここには各行の内容は含まれません。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refsect1><informalexample><screen>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:1044
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"$ svn blame --xml http://svn.red-bean.com/repos/test/readme.txt\n"
"&lt;?xml version=\"1.0\"?&gt;\n"
"&lt;blame&gt;\n"
"&lt;target\n"
"   path=\"readme.txt\"&gt;\n"
"&lt;entry\n"
"   line-number=\"1\"&gt;\n"
"&lt;commit\n"
"   revision=\"3\"&gt;\n"
"&lt;author&gt;sally&lt;/author&gt;\n"
"&lt;date&gt;2008-05-25T19:12:31.428953Z&lt;/date&gt;\n"
"&lt;/commit&gt;\n"
"&lt;/entry&gt;\n"
"&lt;entry\n"
"   line-number=\"2\"&gt;\n"
"&lt;commit\n"
"   revision=\"5\"&gt;\n"
"&lt;author&gt;harry&lt;/author&gt;\n"
"&lt;date&gt;2008-05-29T03:26:12.293121Z&lt;/date&gt;\n"
"&lt;/commit&gt;\n"
"&lt;/entry&gt;\n"
"&lt;/target&gt;\n"
"&lt;/blame&gt;\n"
msgstr ""
"$ svn blame --xml http://svn.red-bean.com/repos/test/readme.txt\n"
"&lt;?xml version=\"1.0\"?&gt;\n"
"&lt;blame&gt;\n"
"&lt;target\n"
"   path=\"readme.txt\"&gt;\n"
"&lt;entry\n"
"   line-number=\"1\"&gt;\n"
"&lt;commit\n"
"   revision=\"3\"&gt;\n"
"&lt;author&gt;sally&lt;/author&gt;\n"
"&lt;date&gt;2008-05-25T19:12:31.428953Z&lt;/date&gt;\n"
"&lt;/commit&gt;\n"
"&lt;/entry&gt;\n"
"&lt;entry\n"
"   line-number=\"2\"&gt;\n"
"&lt;commit\n"
"   revision=\"5\"&gt;\n"
"&lt;author&gt;harry&lt;/author&gt;\n"
"&lt;date&gt;2008-05-29T03:26:12.293121Z&lt;/date&gt;\n"
"&lt;/commit&gt;\n"
"&lt;/entry&gt;\n"
"&lt;/target&gt;\n"
"&lt;/blame&gt;\n"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><indexterm><tertiary>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:1079 en/book/ch09-reference.xml:7675
msgid "cat"
msgstr "cat"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refnamediv><refpurpose>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:1084
msgid "Output the contents of the specified files or URLs."
msgstr "指定したファイルや URL の内容を表示します。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refsect1><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:1089
msgid "<literal>svn cat TARGET[@REV]...</literal>"
msgstr "<literal>svn cat TARGET[@REV]...</literal>"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refsect1><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:1094
msgid ""
"Output the contents of the specified files or URLs.  For listing the "
"contents of directories, see <command>svn list</command> later in this "
"chapter."
msgstr ""
"指定したファイルや URL の内容を表示します。ディレクトリの内容の表示について"
"は、この章で後述する <command>svn list</command> をご覧ください。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refsect1><informalexample><screen>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:1104
#, no-wrap
msgid "--revision (-r) REV\n"
msgstr "--revision (-r) REV\n"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refsect1><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:1112
msgid ""
"If you want to view <filename>readme.txt</filename> in your repository "
"without checking it out:"
msgstr ""
"チェックアウトせずにリポジトリー内の <filename>readme.txt</filename> を表示す"
"る場合、以下のようにします。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refsect1><informalexample><screen>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:1117
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"$ svn cat http://svn.red-bean.com/repos/test/readme.txt\n"
"This is a README file.\n"
"You should read this.\n"
"$\n"
msgstr ""
"$ svn cat http://svn.red-bean.com/repos/test/readme.txt\n"
"This is a README file.\n"
"You should read this.\n"
"$\n"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refsect1><tip><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:1125
msgid ""
"If your working copy is out of date (or you have local modifications) and "
"you want to see the <literal>HEAD</literal> revision of a file in your "
"working copy, <command>svn cat -r HEAD <replaceable>FILENAME</replaceable></"
"command> will automatically fetch the <literal>HEAD</literal> revision of "
"the specified path:"
msgstr ""
"作業コピーが最新ではない (もしくは作業コピーに何か修正を加えた) 場合で、作業"
"コピーのファイルの <literal>HEAD</literal> リビジョンを見る場合、"
"<command>svn cat -r HEAD <replaceable>FILENAME</replaceable></command> は自動"
"的に指定したパスの <literal>HEAD</literal> リビジョンを取得します。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refsect1><informalexample><screen>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:1135
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"$ cat foo.c\n"
"This file is in my local working copy \n"
"and has changes that I've made.\n"
"$ svn cat -r HEAD foo.c\n"
"Latest revision fresh from the repository!\n"
"$\n"
msgstr ""
"$ cat foo.c\n"
"This file is in my local working copy \n"
"and has changes that I've made.\n"
"$ svn cat -r HEAD foo.c\n"
"Latest revision fresh from the repository!\n"
"$\n"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><indexterm><tertiary>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:1153
msgid "changelist"
msgstr "changelist"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refnamediv><refname>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:1157
msgid "svn changelist (cl)"
msgstr "svn changelist (cl)"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refnamediv><refpurpose>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:1158
msgid "Associate (or deassociate) local paths with a changelist."
msgstr "ローカルパスを変更リストに、結合 (分離) を行います。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refsect1><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:1163
msgid "<literal>changelist CLNAME TARGET...</literal>"
msgstr "<literal>changelist CLNAME TARGET...</literal>"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refsect1><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:1164
msgid "<literal>changelist --remove TARGET...</literal>"
msgstr "<literal>changelist --remove TARGET...</literal>"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refsect1><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:1169
msgid ""
"Used for dividing files in a working copy into a changelist (logical named "
"grouping) in order to allow users to easily work on multiple file "
"collections within a single working copy."
msgstr ""
"ひとつの作業コピーにある複数のファイルの集まりを、簡単に扱えるようにするた"
"め、作業コピーの別々のファイルを、変更リスト (論理名のついたグループ) に入れ"
"ます。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refsect1><informalexample><screen>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:1181
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"--changelist ARG\n"
"--depth ARG\n"
"--quiet (-q)\n"
"--recursive (-R)\n"
"--remove\n"
"--targets FILENAME\n"
msgstr ""
"--changelist ARG\n"
"--depth ARG\n"
"--quiet (-q)\n"
"--recursive (-R)\n"
"--remove\n"
"--targets FILENAME\n"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refsect1><title>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:1192 en/book/ch09-reference.xml:8538
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:10167
msgid "Example"
msgstr "例"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refsect1><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:1194
msgid ""
"Edit three files, add them to a changelist, then commit only files in that "
"changelist:"
msgstr ""
"3 ファイルを編集し変更リストに入れます。それから次のように変更リストのファイ"
"ルのみをコミットします。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refsect1><informalexample><screen>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:1199
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"$ svn changelist issue1729 foo.c bar.c baz.c\n"
"A [issue1729] foo.c\n"
"A [issue1729] bar.c\n"
"A [issue1729] baz.c\n"
"$ svn status\n"
"A       someotherfile.c\n"
"A       test/sometest.c\n"
"\n"
"--- Changelist 'issue1729':\n"
"A       foo.c\n"
"A       bar.c\n"
"A       baz.c\n"
"$ svn commit --changelist issue1729 -m \"Fixing Issue 1729.\"\n"
"Adding         bar.c\n"
"Adding         baz.c\n"
"Adding         foo.c\n"
"Transmitting file data ...\n"
"Committed revision 2.\n"
"$ svn status\n"
"A       someotherfile.c\n"
"A       test/sometest.c\n"
"$\n"
msgstr ""
"$ svn changelist issue1729 foo.c bar.c baz.c\n"
"A [issue1729] foo.c\n"
"A [issue1729] bar.c\n"
"A [issue1729] baz.c\n"
"$ svn status\n"
"A       someotherfile.c\n"
"A       test/sometest.c\n"
"\n"
"--- 変更リスト 'issue1729':\n"
"A       foo.c\n"
"A       bar.c\n"
"A       baz.c\n"
"$ svn commit --changelist issue1729 -m \"Fixing Issue 1729.\"\n"
"Adding         bar.c\n"
"Adding         baz.c\n"
"Adding         foo.c\n"
"ファイルのデータを送信しています ...\n"
"リビジョン 2 をコミットしました。\n"
"$ svn status\n"
"A       someotherfile.c\n"
"A       test/sometest.c\n"
"$\n"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refsect1><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:1224
msgid ""
"Note that in the previous example, only the files in changelist "
"<literal>issue1729</literal> were committed."
msgstr ""
"前述の例では、変更リスト <replaceable>issue1729</replaceable> にあるファイル"
"だけをコミットすることに注意してください。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refnamediv><refname>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:1241
msgid "svn checkout (co)"
msgstr "svn checkout (co)"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refnamediv><refpurpose>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:1242
msgid "Check out a working copy from a repository."
msgstr "リポジトリーから作業コピーをチェックアウトします。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refsect1><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:1246
msgid "<literal>svn checkout URL[@REV]... [PATH]</literal>"
msgstr "<literal>svn checkout URL[@REV]... [PATH]</literal>"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refsect1><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:1251
msgid ""
"Check out a working copy from a repository.  If <replaceable>PATH</"
"replaceable> is omitted, the basename of the URL will be used as the "
"destination.  If multiple URLs are given, each will be checked out into a "
"subdirectory of <replaceable>PATH</replaceable>, with the name of the "
"subdirectory being the basename of the URL."
msgstr ""
"リポジトリーから作業コピーをチェックアウトします。 <replaceable>PATH</"
"replaceable> を省略すると、コピー先として URL のベース名を使用します。複数の "
"URL を指定すると、それぞれ <replaceable>PATH</replaceable> のサブディレクトリ"
"にチェックアウトしますが、サブディレクトリの名前は URL のベース名になります。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refsect1><informalexample><screen>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:1266
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"--depth ARG\n"
"--force\n"
"--ignore-externals\n"
"--quiet (-q)\n"
"--revision (-r) REV\n"
msgstr ""
"--depth ARG\n"
"--force\n"
"--ignore-externals\n"
"--quiet (-q)\n"
"--revision (-r) REV\n"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refsect1><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:1278
msgid ""
"Check out a working copy into a directory called <filename>mine</filename>:"
msgstr ""
"<filename>mine</filename> と呼ばれるディレクトリに、作業コピーをチェックアウ"
"トします。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refsect1><informalexample><screen>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:1283
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"$ svn checkout file:///var/svn/repos/test mine\n"
"A    mine/a\n"
"A    mine/b\n"
"A    mine/c\n"
"A    mine/d\n"
"Checked out revision 20.\n"
"$ ls\n"
"mine\n"
"$\n"
msgstr ""
"$ svn checkout file:///var/svn/repos/test mine\n"
"A    mine/a\n"
"A    mine/b\n"
"A    mine/c\n"
"A    mine/d\n"
"リビジョン 20 をチェックアウトしました。\n"
"$ ls\n"
"mine\n"
"$\n"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refsect1><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:1295
msgid "Check out two different directories into two separate working copies:"
msgstr ""
"二つの異なるディレクトリを、二つの別々の作業コピーにチェックアウトします。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refsect1><informalexample><screen>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:1300
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"$ svn checkout file:///var/svn/repos/test \\\n"
"               file:///var/svn/repos/quiz\n"
"A    test/a\n"
"A    test/b\n"
"A    test/c\n"
"A    test/d\n"
"Checked out revision 20.\n"
"A    quiz/l\n"
"A    quiz/m\n"
"Checked out revision 13.\n"
"$ ls\n"
"quiz  test\n"
"$\n"
msgstr ""
"$ svn checkout file:///var/svn/repos/test \\\n"
"               file:///var/svn/repos/quiz\n"
"A    test/a\n"
"A    test/b\n"
"A    test/c\n"
"A    test/d\n"
"リビジョン 20 をチェックアウトしました。\n"
"A    quiz/l\n"
"A    quiz/m\n"
"リビジョン 13 をチェックアウトしました。\n"
"$ ls\n"
"quiz  test\n"
"$\n"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refsect1><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:1316
msgid ""
"Check out two different directories into two separate working copies, but "
"place both into a directory called <filename>working-copies</filename>:"
msgstr ""
"二つの異なるディレクトリを、二つの別々の作業コピーにチェックアウトするが、両"
"方とも <filename>working-copies</filename> というディレクトリ内に作ります。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refsect1><informalexample><screen>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:1322
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"$ svn checkout file:///var/svn/repos/test \\\n"
"               file:///var/svn/repos/quiz \\\n"
"               working-copies\n"
"A    working-copies/test/a\n"
"A    working-copies/test/b\n"
"A    working-copies/test/c\n"
"A    working-copies/test/d\n"
"Checked out revision 20.\n"
"A    working-copies/quiz/l\n"
"A    working-copies/quiz/m\n"
"Checked out revision 13.\n"
"$ ls\n"
"working-copies\n"
msgstr ""
"$ svn checkout file:///var/svn/repos/test \\\n"
"               file:///var/svn/repos/quiz \\\n"
"               working-copies\n"
"A    working-copies/test/a\n"
"A    working-copies/test/b\n"
"A    working-copies/test/c\n"
"A    working-copies/test/d\n"
"リビジョン 20 をチェックアウトしました。\n"
"A    working-copies/quiz/l\n"
"A    working-copies/quiz/m\n"
"リビジョン 13 をチェックアウトしました。\n"
"$ ls\n"
"working-copies\n"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refsect1><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:1338
msgid ""
"If you interrupt a checkout (or something else interrupts your checkout, "
"such as loss of connectivity, etc.), you can restart it either by issuing "
"the identical checkout command again or by updating the incomplete working "
"copy:"
msgstr ""
"チェックアウトを中断する (もしくは、接続が切れてチェックアウトが中断された) "
"場合、もう一度純粋なチェックアウトコマンドを実行しても、不完全な作業コピーを"
"更新しても再開できます。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refsect1><informalexample><screen>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:1346
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"$ svn checkout file:///var/svn/repos/test mine\n"
"A    mine/a\n"
"A    mine/b\n"
"^C\n"
"svn: E200015: Caught signal\n"
"$ svn checkout file:///var/svn/repos/test mine\n"
"A    mine/c\n"
"^C\n"
"svn: E200015: Caught signal\n"
"$ svn update mine\n"
"Updating 'mine':\n"
"A    mine/d\n"
"Updated to revision 20.\n"
"$\n"
msgstr ""
"$ svn checkout file:///var/svn/repos/test mine\n"
"A    mine/a\n"
"A    mine/b\n"
"^C\n"
"svn: E200015: シグナルを受け取りました\n"
"$ svn checkout file:///var/svn/repos/test mine\n"
"A    mine/c\n"
"^C\n"
"svn: E200015: シグナルを受け取りました\n"
"$ svn update mine\n"
"Updating 'mine':\n"
"A    mine/d\n"
"リビジョン 20 に更新しました。\n"
"$\n"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refsect1><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:1363
msgid ""
"If you wish to check out some revision other than the most recent one, you "
"can do so by providing the <option>--revision</option> (<option>-r</option>) "
"option to the <command>svn checkout</command> command:"
msgstr ""
"最新のものではなく、リビジョンを指定してチェックアウトしたければ、"
"<command>svn checkout</command> コマンドに <option>--revision</option> "
"(<option>-r</option>) オプションを指定して実行できます。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refsect1><informalexample><screen>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:1370
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"$ svn checkout -r 2 file:///var/svn/repos/test mine\n"
"A    mine/a\n"
"Checked out revision 2.\n"
"$\n"
msgstr ""
"$ svn checkout -r 2 file:///var/svn/repos/test mine\n"
"A    mine/a\n"
"リビジョン 2 をチェックアウトしました。\n"
"$\n"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refsect1><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:1377
msgid ""
"Prior to version 1.7, Subversion would complain by default if you try to "
"check out a directory atop an existing directory which contains files or "
"subdirectories that the checkout itself would have created.  Subversion 1.7 "
"handles this situation differently, allowing the checkout to proceed but "
"marking any obstructing objects as tree conflicts.  Use the <option>--force</"
"option> option to override this safeguard.  When you check out with the "
"<option>--force</option> option, any unversioned file in the checkout target "
"tree which ordinarily would obstruct the checkout will still become "
"versioned, but Subversion will preserve its contents as-is.  If those "
"contents differ from the repository file at that path (which was downloaded "
"as part of the checkout), the file will appear to have local "
"modifications&mdash;the changes required to transform the versioned file you "
"checked out into the unversioned file you had before checking out&mdash;when "
"the checkout completes."
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refsect1><informalexample><screen>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:1398
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"$ mkdir project\n"
"$ mkdir project/lib\n"
"$ touch project/lib/file.c\n"
"$ svn checkout file:///var/svn/repos/project/trunk project --force\n"
"E    project/lib\n"
"A    project/lib/subdir\n"
"E    project/lib/file.c\n"
"A    project/lib/anotherfile.c\n"
"A    project/include/header.h\n"
"Checked out revision 21.\n"
"$ svn status wc\n"
"M       project/lib/file.c\n"
"$ svn diff wc\n"
"Index: project/lib/file.c\n"
"===================================================================\n"
"--- project/lib/file.c\t(revision 1)\n"
"+++ project/lib/file.c\t(working copy)\n"
"@@ -3 +0,0 @@\n"
"-/* file.c: Code for acting file-ishly. */\n"
"-#include &lt;stdio.h&gt;\n"
"-/* Not feeling particularly creative today. */\n"
"\n"
"$\n"
msgstr ""
"$ mkdir project\n"
"$ mkdir project/lib\n"
"$ touch project/lib/file.c\n"
"$ svn checkout file:///var/svn/repos/project/trunk project --force\n"
"E    project/lib\n"
"A    project/lib/subdir\n"
"E    project/lib/file.c\n"
"A    project/lib/anotherfile.c\n"
"A    project/include/header.h\n"
"Checked out revision 21.\n"
"$ svn status wc\n"
"M       project/lib/file.c\n"
"$ svn diff wc\n"
"Index: project/lib/file.c\n"
"===================================================================\n"
"--- project/lib/file.c\t(リビジョン 1)\n"
"+++ project/lib/file.c\t(作業コピー)\n"
"@@ -3 +0,0 @@\n"
"-/* file.c: Code for acting file-ishly. */\n"
"-#include &lt;stdio.h&gt;\n"
"-/* Not feeling particularly creative today. */\n"
"\n"
"$\n"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refsect1><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:1424
msgid ""
"As in another other working copy, you have the choices typically available: "
"reverting some or all of those local <quote>modifications</quote>, "
"committing them, or continuing to modify your working copy."
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refsect1><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:1429
msgid ""
"This feature is especially useful for performing in-place imports of "
"unversioned directory trees.  By first importing the tree into the "
"repository, and then checking out new repository location atop the "
"unversioned tree with the <option>--force</option> option, you effectively "
"transform the unversioned tree into a working copy."
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refsect1><informalexample><screen>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:1439
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"$ svn mkdir -m \"Create newproject project root.\" \\\n"
"      file://var/svn/repos/newproject\n"
"$ svn import -m \"Import initial newproject codebase.\" newproject \\\n"
"      file://var/svn/repos/newproject/trunk\n"
"Adding         newproject/include\n"
"Adding         newproject/include/newproject.h\n"
"Adding         newproject/lib\n"
"Adding         newproject/lib/helpers.c\n"
"Adding         newproject/lib/base.c\n"
"Adding         newproject/notes\n"
"Adding         newproject/notes/README\n"
"\n"
"Committed revision 22.\n"
"$ svn checkout file://`pwd`/repos-1.6/newproject/trunk newproject --force\n"
"E    newproject/include\n"
"E    newproject/include/newproject.h\n"
"E    newproject/lib\n"
"E    newproject/lib/helpers.c\n"
"E    newproject/lib/base.c\n"
"E    newproject/notes\n"
"E    newproject/notes/README\n"
"Checked out revision 2.\n"
"$ svn status newproject\n"
"$\n"
msgstr ""
"$ svn mkdir -m \"Create newproject project root.\" \\\n"
"      file://var/svn/repos/newproject\n"
"$ svn import -m \"Import initial newproject codebase.\" newproject \\\n"
"      file://var/svn/repos/newproject/trunk\n"
"Adding         newproject/include\n"
"Adding         newproject/include/newproject.h\n"
"Adding         newproject/lib\n"
"Adding         newproject/lib/helpers.c\n"
"Adding         newproject/lib/base.c\n"
"Adding         newproject/notes\n"
"Adding         newproject/notes/README\n"
"\n"
"リビジョン 22 をコミットしました。\n"
"$ svn checkout file://`pwd`/repos-1.6/newproject/trunk newproject --force\n"
"E    newproject/include\n"
"E    newproject/include/newproject.h\n"
"E    newproject/lib\n"
"E    newproject/lib/helpers.c\n"
"E    newproject/lib/base.c\n"
"E    newproject/notes\n"
"E    newproject/notes/README\n"
"リビジョン 2 をチェックアウトしました。\n"
"$ svn status newproject\n"
"$\n"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><indexterm><tertiary>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:1475
msgid "cleanup"
msgstr "cleanup"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refnamediv><refname>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:1479
msgid "svn cleanup"
msgstr "svn cleanup"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refnamediv><refpurpose>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:1480
msgid "Recursively clean up the working copy"
msgstr "作業コピーを再帰的に掃除する"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refsect1><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:1484
msgid "<literal>svn cleanup [PATH...]</literal>"
msgstr "<literal>svn cleanup [PATH...]</literal>"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refsect1><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:1489
msgid ""
"Recursively clean up the working copy, removing working copy locks and "
"resuming unfinished operations.  If you ever get a <literal>working copy "
"locked</literal> error, run this command to remove stale locks and get your "
"working copy into a usable state again."
msgstr ""
"作業コピーを再帰的に片付け、作業コピーのロック削除と未完了操作の継続を行いま"
"す。<literal>作業コピーのロック</literal>エラーが発生した際は、このコマンドを"
"実行して、古くなったロックを削除し、作業コピーを使用できる状態にしてくださ"
"い。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refsect1><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:1495
msgid ""
"If, for some reason, an <command>svn update</command> fails due to a problem "
"running an external diff program (e.g., user input or network failure), pass "
"the <option>--diff3-cmd</option> to allow cleanup to complete any merging "
"with your external diff program.  You can also specify any configuration "
"directory with the <option>--config-dir</option> option, but you should need "
"these options extremely infrequently."
msgstr ""
"何らかの理由で、外部 diff プログラム の実行時の問題 (例: ユーザー入力やネット"
"ワークの問題など) が原因で <command>svn update</command> が失敗する場合、マー"
"ジ処理を完了するため片付けるのに、<option>--diff3-cmd</option> で外部 diff プ"
"ログラムを渡してください。また <option>--config-dir</option> オプションで任意"
"の設定ディレクトリの指定もできます。ただしこれらのオプションが必要な場面はほ"
"とんどありません。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refsect1><informalexample><screen>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:1511
#, no-wrap
msgid "--diff3-cmd CMD\n"
msgstr "--diff3-cmd CMD\n"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refsect1><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:1520
msgid ""
"Well, there's not much to the examples here, as <command>svn cleanup</"
"command> generates no output.  If you pass no <replaceable>PATH</"
"replaceable>, then <quote><filename>.</filename></quote> is used:"
msgstr ""
"<command>svn cleanup</command> は何も出力しないので、あまり例はありません。"
"<replaceable>PATH</replaceable> を指定しない場合、<quote><filename>.</"
"filename></quote> を使用します。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refsect1><informalexample><screen>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:1527
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"$ svn cleanup\n"
"$ svn cleanup /var/svn/working-copy\n"
msgstr ""
"$ svn cleanup\n"
"$ svn cleanup /var/svn/working-copy\n"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refnamediv><refname>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:1545
msgid "svn commit (ci)"
msgstr "svn commit (ci)"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refnamediv><refpurpose>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:1546
msgid "Send changes from your working copy to the repository."
msgstr "作業コピーの変更点をリポジトリーに送ります。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refsect1><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:1550
msgid "<literal>svn commit [PATH...]</literal>"
msgstr "<literal>svn commit [PATH...]</literal>"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refsect1><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:1555
msgid ""
"Send changes from your working copy to the repository.  If you do not supply "
"a log message with your commit by using either the <option>--file</option> "
"(<option>-F</option>) or <option>--message</option> (<option>-m</option>) "
"option, <command>svn</command> will launch your editor for you to compose a "
"commit message.  See the <literal>editor-cmd</literal> list entry in <xref "
"linkend=\"svn.advanced.confarea.opts.config\"/>."
msgstr ""
"作業コピーの変更点をリポジトリーに送ります。<option>--file</option> "
"(<option>-F</option>) や <option>--message</option> (<option>-m</option>) オ"
"プションを指定して、コミットにログメッセージを指定しない場合、コミットメッ"
"セージを作成するため、<command>svn</command> はエディタを起動します。<xref "
"linkend=\"svn.advanced.confarea.opts.config\"/> にある <literal>editor-cmd</"
"literal> リストエントリをご覧ください。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refsect1><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:1565
msgid ""
"<command>svn commit</command> will send any lock tokens that it finds and "
"will release locks on all <replaceable>PATH</replaceable>s committed "
"(recursively)  unless <option>--no-unlock</option> is passed."
msgstr ""
"<command>svn commit</command> は、<option>--no-unlock</option> を指定しなけれ"
"ば、見つかったロックトークンを送信し、コミットされたすべての "
"<replaceable>PATHS</replaceable> 上にあるロックを (再帰的に) 開放します。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refsect1><tip><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:1571
msgid ""
"If you begin a commit and Subversion launches your editor to compose the "
"commit message, you can still abort without committing your changes.  If you "
"want to cancel your commit, just quit your editor without saving your commit "
"message and Subversion will prompt you to either abort the commit, continue "
"with no message, or edit the message again."
msgstr ""
"コミットを始め、Subversion がメッセージ作成のためのエディタを起動した後でも、"
"まだ変更をコミットせず中断できます。コミットを取り消す場合、コミットメッセー"
"ジを保存せず、単にエディタを終了してください。Subversion はコミットを中断する"
"か、メッセージなしで継続するか、メッセージを再編集するかを聞いてきます。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refsect1><informalexample><screen>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:1587
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"--changelist ARG\n"
"--depth ARG\n"
"--editor-cmd CMD\n"
"--encoding ENC\n"
"--file (-F) FILENAME\n"
"--force-log\n"
"--keep-changelists\n"
"--message (-m) MESSAGE\n"
"--no-unlock\n"
"--quiet (-q)\n"
"--targets FILENAME\n"
"--with-revprop ARG\n"
msgstr ""
"--changelist ARG\n"
"--depth ARG\n"
"--editor-cmd CMD\n"
"--encoding ENC\n"
"--file (-F) FILENAME\n"
"--force-log\n"
"--keep-changelists\n"
"--message (-m) MESSAGE\n"
"--no-unlock\n"
"--quiet (-q)\n"
"--targets FILENAME\n"
"--with-revprop ARG\n"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refsect1><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:1606
msgid ""
"Commit a simple modification to a file with the commit message on the "
"command line and an implicit target of your current directory "
"(<quote><filename>.</filename></quote>):"
msgstr ""
"コマンドラインで指定したコミットメッセージとカレントディレクトリ "
"(<quote><filename>.</filename></quote>) を、暗黙のターゲットとして単純な変更"
"をコミットします。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refsect1><informalexample><screen>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:1613
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"$ svn commit -m \"added howto section.\"\n"
"Sending        a\n"
"Transmitting file data .\n"
"Committed revision 3.\n"
msgstr ""
"$ svn commit -m \"added howto section.\"\n"
"Sending        a\n"
"ファイルのデータを送信しています\n"
"リビジョン 3 をコミットしました。\n"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refsect1><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:1620
msgid ""
"Commit a modification to the file <filename>foo.c</filename> (explicitly "
"specified on the command line) with the commit message in a file named "
"<filename>msg</filename>:"
msgstr ""
"ファイル <filename>foo.c</filename> (コマンドラインに明示) の変更点を、ファイ"
"ル <filename>msg</filename> の内容をコミットメッセージとしてコミットします。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refsect1><informalexample><screen>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:1627
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"$ svn commit -F msg foo.c\n"
"Sending        foo.c\n"
"Transmitting file data .\n"
"Committed revision 5.\n"
msgstr ""
"$ svn commit -F msg foo.c\n"
"Sending        foo.c\n"
"ファイルのデータを送信しています .\n"
"リビジョン 5 をコミットしました。\n"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refsect1><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:1634
msgid ""
"If you want to use a file that's under version control for your commit "
"message with <option>--file</option> (<option>-F</option>), you need to pass "
"the <option>--force-log</option> option:"
msgstr ""
"バージョン管理下にあるファイルを、<option>--file</option> (<option>-F</"
"option>) でコミットメッセージとして指定したい場合、以下のように、<option>--"
"force-log</option> オプションを渡す必要があります。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refsect1><informalexample><screen>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:1641
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"$ svn commit -F file_under_vc.txt foo.c\n"
"svn: E205004: Log message file is a versioned file; use '--force-log' to override\n"
"\n"
"$ svn commit --force-log -F file_under_vc.txt foo.c\n"
"Sending        foo.c\n"
"Transmitting file data .\n"
"Committed revision 6.\n"
msgstr ""
"$ svn commit -F file_under_vc.txt foo.c\n"
"svn: E205004: ログメッセージファイルがバージョン管理されているファイルです。無効にするには '--force-log' を用いてください\n"
"\n"
"$ svn commit --force-log -F file_under_vc.txt foo.c\n"
"送信しています              foo.c\n"
"ファイルのデータを送信しています .\n"
"リビジョン 6 をコミットしました。\n"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refsect1><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:1651
msgid "To commit a file scheduled for deletion:"
msgstr "削除準備したファイルをコミットするには以下のようにします。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refsect1><informalexample><screen>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:1655
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"$ svn commit -m \"removed file 'c'.\"\n"
"Deleting       c\n"
"\n"
"Committed revision 7.\n"
msgstr ""
"$ svn commit -m \"removed file 'c'.\"\n"
"Deleting       c\n"
"\n"
"リビジョン 7 をコミットしました。\n"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refnamediv><refname>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:1675
msgid "svn copy (cp)"
msgstr "svn copy (cp)"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refnamediv><refpurpose>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:1676
msgid "Copy a file or directory in a working copy or in the repository."
msgstr "作業コピーやリポジトリー中の、ファイルやディレクトリをコピーします。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refsect1><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:1682
msgid "<literal>svn copy SRC[@REV]... DST</literal>"
msgstr "<literal>svn copy SRC[@REV]... DST</literal>"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refsect1><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:1688
msgid ""
"Copy one or more files in a working copy or in the repository. "
"<replaceable>SRC</replaceable> and <replaceable>DST</replaceable> can each "
"be either a working copy (WC) path or URL.  When copying multiple sources, "
"add the copies as immediate children of <replaceable>DST</replaceable> "
"(which, of course, must be a directory)."
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refsect1><variablelist><varlistentry><term>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:1699 en/book/ch09-reference.xml:3689
msgid "WC &rarr; WC"
msgstr "WC &rarr; WC"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refsect1><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:1701
