msgstr "URL &rarr; WC"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refsect1><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:1716
msgid "Check out URL into WC and schedule it for addition."
msgstr "URL を WC にチェックアウトし、追加準備をします。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refsect1><variablelist><varlistentry><term>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:1722 en/book/ch09-reference.xml:3697
msgid "URL &rarr; URL"
msgstr "URL &rarr; URL"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refsect1><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:1724
msgid "Complete server-side copy.  This is usually used to branch and tag."
msgstr "完全なサーバー上でのコピーです。通常ブランチやタグに利用します。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refsect1><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:1731
msgid ""
"If no peg revision (i.e., <replaceable>@REV</replaceable>) is supplied, by "
"default the <literal>BASE</literal> revision will be used for files copied "
"from the working copy, while the <literal>HEAD</literal> revision will be "
"used for files copied from a URL."
msgstr ""
"peg リビジョン (例: <replaceable>@REV</replaceable>) を指定しないと、デフォル"
"トでは、作業コピーからコピーする場合は、<literal>BASE</literal> リビジョンを"
"用い、URL からコピーする場合は <literal>HEAD</literal> リビジョンを用います。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refsect1><note><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:1739
msgid ""
"You can only copy files within a single repository.  Subversion does not "
"support cross-repository copying."
msgstr ""
"ファイルはひとつのリポジトリー内でのみコピーできます。Subversion はリポジト"
"リー間コピーをサポートしていません。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refsect1><informalexample><screen>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:1750
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"--editor-cmd CMD\n"
"--encoding ENC\n"
"--file (-F) FILENAME\n"
"--force-log\n"
"--ignore-externals\n"
"--message (-m) MESSAGE\n"
"--parents\n"
"--quiet (-q)\n"
"--revision (-r) REV\n"
"--with-revprop ARG\n"
msgstr ""
"--editor-cmd CMD\n"
"--encoding ENC\n"
"--file (-F) FILENAME\n"
"--force-log\n"
"--ignore-externals\n"
"--message (-m) MESSAGE\n"
"--parents\n"
"--quiet (-q)\n"
"--revision (-r) REV\n"
"--with-revprop ARG\n"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refsect1><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:1767
msgid ""
"Copy an item within your working copy (this schedules the copy&mdash;nothing "
"goes into the repository until you commit):"
msgstr ""
"作業コピー中の項目をコピーします (コピー準備のみ&mdash;次のコミットまでリポジ"
"トリーには何も起こりません)。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refsect1><informalexample><screen>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:1773
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"$ svn copy foo.txt bar.txt\n"
"A         bar.txt\n"
"$ svn status\n"
"A  +    bar.txt\n"
msgstr ""
"$ svn copy foo.txt bar.txt\n"
"A         bar.txt\n"
"$ svn status\n"
"A  +    bar.txt\n"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refsect1><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:1780
msgid "Copy several files in a working copy into a subdirectory:"
msgstr "作業コピー内の、複数のファイルをサブディレクトリにコピーします。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refsect1><informalexample><screen>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:1785
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"$ svn copy bat.c baz.c qux.c src\n"
"A         src/bat.c\n"
"A         src/baz.c\n"
"A         src/qux.c\n"
msgstr ""
"$ svn copy bat.c baz.c qux.c src\n"
"A         src/bat.c\n"
"A         src/baz.c\n"
"A         src/qux.c\n"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refsect1><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:1792
msgid ""
"Copy revision 8 of <filename>bat.c</filename> into your working copy under a "
"different name:"
msgstr ""
"<filename>bat.c</filename> のリビジョン 8 を、作業コピーに別の名前でコピーし"
"ます。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refsect1><informalexample><screen>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:1797
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"$ svn copy -r 8 bat.c ya-old-bat.c\n"
"A         ya-old-bat.c\n"
msgstr ""
"$ svn copy -r 8 bat.c ya-old-bat.c\n"
"A         ya-old-bat.c\n"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refsect1><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:1802
msgid ""
"Copy an item in your working copy to a URL in the repository (this is an "
"immediate commit, so you must supply a commit message):"
msgstr ""
"リポジトリー内の URL に、作業コピー内の項目をコピーします (同時にコミットされ"
"るので、コミットメッセージを指定する必要あります)。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refsect1><informalexample><screen>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:1808
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"$ svn copy near.txt file:///var/svn/repos/test/far-away.txt -m \"Remote copy.\"\n"
"\n"
"Committed revision 8.\n"
msgstr ""
"$ svn copy near.txt file:///var/svn/repos/test/far-away.txt -m \"Remote copy.\"\n"
"\n"
"リビジョン 8 をコミットしました。\n"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refsect1><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:1814
msgid ""
"Copy an item from the repository to your working copy (this just schedules "
"the copy&mdash;nothing goes into the repository until you commit):"
msgstr ""
"リポジトリーの項目を作業コピーにコピーします (コピー準備のみ&mdash;次のコミッ"
"トまでリポジトリーには何も起こりません)。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refsect1><informalexample><screen>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:1820
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"$ svn copy file:///var/svn/repos/test/far-away -r 6 near-here\n"
"A         near-here\n"
msgstr ""
"$ svn copy file:///var/svn/repos/test/far-away -r 6 near-here\n"
"A         near-here\n"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refsect1><tip><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:1826
msgid ""
"This is the recommended way to resurrect a dead file in your repository!"
msgstr ""
"これはリポジトリー中の死んだファイルを復活させるのにおすすめの方法です!"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refsect1><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:1830
msgid "And finally, copy between two URLs:"
msgstr "そして最後に、二つの URL の間でコピーします。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refsect1><informalexample><screen>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:1834
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"$ svn copy file:///var/svn/repos/test/far-away \\\n"
"           file:///var/svn/repos/test/over-there -m \"remote copy.\"\n"
"\n"
"Committed revision 9.\n"
msgstr ""
"$ svn copy file:///var/svn/repos/test/far-away \\\n"
"           file:///var/svn/repos/test/over-there -m \"remote copy.\"\n"
"\n"
"リビジョン 9 をコミットしました。\n"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refsect1><informalexample><screen>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:1843
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"$ svn copy file:///var/svn/repos/test/trunk \\\n"
"           file:///var/svn/repos/test/tags/0.6.32-prerelease -m \"tag tree\"\n"
"\n"
"Committed revision 12.\n"
msgstr ""
"$ svn copy file:///var/svn/repos/test/trunk \\\n"
"           file:///var/svn/repos/test/tags/0.6.32-prerelease -m \"tag tree\"\n"
"\n"
"リビジョン 12 をコミットしました。\n"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refsect1><tip><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:1851
msgid ""
"This is the easiest way to <quote>tag</quote> a revision in your "
"repository&mdash;just <command>svn copy</command> that revision (usually "
"<literal>HEAD</literal>) into your <filename>tags</filename> directory."
msgstr ""
"リポジトリー中のリビジョンに <quote>tag</quote> をつける一番簡単な方法は "
"&mdash; そのリビジョン (通常 <literal>HEAD</literal>) を <filename>tags</"
"filename> ディレクトリに、単に <command>svn copy</command> することです。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refsect1><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:1857
msgid ""
"And don't worry if you forgot to tag&mdash;you can always specify an older "
"revision and tag anytime:"
msgstr ""
"タグの付け忘れを心配する必要はありません&mdash; いつでも古いリビジョンを指定"
"してタグ付けできます。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refsect1><informalexample><screen>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:1862
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"$ svn copy -r 11 file:///var/svn/repos/test/trunk \\\n"
"           file:///var/svn/repos/test/tags/0.6.32-prerelease \\\n"
"           -m \"Forgot to tag at rev 11\"\n"
"\n"
"Committed revision 13.\n"
msgstr ""
"$ svn copy -r 11 file:///var/svn/repos/test/trunk \\\n"
"           file:///var/svn/repos/test/tags/0.6.32-prerelease \\\n"
"           -m \"Forgot to tag at rev 11\"\n"
"\n"
"リビジョン 13 をコミットしました。\n"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refnamediv><refname>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:1882
msgid "svn delete (del, remove, rm)"
msgstr "svn delete (del, remove, rm)"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refnamediv><refpurpose>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:1883
msgid "Delete an item from a working copy or the repository."
msgstr "作業コピーやリポジトリーから項目を削除します。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refsect1><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:1888
msgid "<literal>svn delete PATH...</literal>"
msgstr "<literal>svn delete PATH...</literal>"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refsect1><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:1889
msgid "<literal>svn delete URL...</literal>"
msgstr "<literal>svn delete URL...</literal>"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refsect1><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:1894
msgid ""
"Items specified by <replaceable>PATH</replaceable> are scheduled for "
"deletion upon the next commit.  Files (and directories that have not been "
"committed) are immediately removed from the working copy unless the "
"<option>--keep-local</option> option is given.  The command will not remove "
"any unversioned or modified items; use the <option>--force</option> option "
"to override this behavior."
msgstr ""
"<replaceable>PATH</replaceable> で指定した項目を、次のコミットで削除するよう"
"準備します。<option>--keep-local</option> オプションを与えない限り、ファイル "
"(および、まだコミットしていないディレクトリ) は、直ちに作業コピーから削除され"
"ます。このコマンドはバージョン管理外のものや、修正されているものに対しては動"
"作しません。この動作を上書きするなら、<option>--force</option> スイッチを使っ"
"てください。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refsect1><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:1903
msgid ""
"Items specified by URL are deleted from the repository via an immediate "
"commit.  Multiple URLs are committed atomically."
msgstr ""
"URL で指定された項目は、直接コミットを発行する形で削除されます。複数の URL は"
"不可分コミットされます。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refsect1><informalexample><screen>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:1913
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"--editor-cmd CMD\n"
"--encoding ENC\n"
"--file (-F) FILENAME\n"
"--force\n"
"--force-log\n"
"--keep-local\n"
"--message (-m) MESSAGE\n"
"--quiet (-q)\n"
"--targets FILENAME\n"
"--with-revprop ARG\n"
msgstr ""
"--editor-cmd CMD\n"
"--encoding ENC\n"
"--file (-F) FILENAME\n"
"--force\n"
"--force-log\n"
"--keep-local\n"
"--message (-m) MESSAGE\n"
"--quiet (-q)\n"
"--targets FILENAME\n"
"--with-revprop ARG\n"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refsect1><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:1930
msgid ""
"Using <command>svn</command> to delete a file from your working copy deletes "
"your local copy of the file, but it merely schedules the file to be deleted "
"from the repository.  When you commit, the file is deleted in the repository."
msgstr ""
"作業コピーからファイルを削除するのに <command>svn</command> を使うと、ファイ"
"ルのローカルコピーが削除されますが、リポジトリーからは単に削除準備がされるだ"
"けです。次回コミット時に、ファイルはリポジトリーから削除されます。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refsect1><informalexample><screen>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:1938
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"$ svn delete myfile\n"
"D         myfile\n"
"\n"
"$ svn commit -m \"Deleted file 'myfile'.\"\n"
"Deleting       myfile\n"
"Transmitting file data .\n"
"Committed revision 14.\n"
msgstr ""
"$ svn delete myfile\n"
"D         myfile\n"
"\n"
"$ svn commit -m \"Deleted file 'myfile'.\"\n"
"Deleting       myfile\n"
"ファイルのデータを送信しています\n"
"リビジョン 14 をコミットしました。\n"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refsect1><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:1948
msgid ""
"Deleting a URL, however, is immediate, so you have to supply a log message:"
msgstr ""
"URL を削除しますが、即時実行のため、ログメッセージを指定する必要があります。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refsect1><informalexample><screen>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:1953
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"$ svn delete -m \"Deleting file 'yourfile'\" \\\n"
"             file:///var/svn/repos/test/yourfile\n"
"\n"
"Committed revision 15.\n"
msgstr ""
"$ svn delete -m \"Deleting file 'yourfile'\" \\\n"
"             file:///var/svn/repos/test/yourfile\n"
"\n"
"リビジョン 15 をコミットしました。\n"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refsect1><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:1960
msgid ""
"Here's an example of how to force deletion of a file that has local mods:"
msgstr "この例は、作業コピーに修正があるファイルを強制削除する方法です。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refsect1><informalexample><screen>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:1965
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"$ svn delete over-there \n"
"svn: E195006: Use --force to override this restriction (local modifications ma\n"
"y be lost)\n"
"svn: E195006: '/home/sally/project/over-there' has local modifications -- comm\n"
"it or revert them first\n"
"$ svn delete --force over-there \n"
"D         over-there\n"
"$\n"
msgstr ""
"$ svn delete over-there \n"
"svn: E195006: Use --force to override this restriction (local modifications ma\n"
"y be lost)\n"
"svn: E195006: '/home/sally/project/over-there' has local modifications -- comm\n"
"it or revert them first\n"
"$ svn delete --force over-there \n"
"D         over-there\n"
"$\n"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refnamediv><refname>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:1989
msgid "svn diff (di)"
msgstr "svn diff (di)"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refnamediv><refpurpose>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:1990
msgid "This displays the differences between two revisions or paths."
msgstr "二つのパスやリビジョン間の差分を表示します。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refsect1><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:1994
msgid "<literal>diff [-c M | -r N[:M]] [TARGET[@REV]...]</literal>"
msgstr "<literal>diff [-c M | -r N[:M]] [TARGET[@REV]...]</literal>"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refsect1><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:1995
msgid ""
"<literal>diff [-r N[:M]] --old=OLD-TGT[@OLDREV] [--new=NEW-TGT[@NEWREV]] "
"[PATH...]</literal>"
msgstr ""
"<literal>diff [-r N[:M]] --old=OLD-TGT[@OLDREV] [--new=NEW-TGT[@NEWREV]] "
"[PATH...]</literal>"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refsect1><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:1996
msgid "<literal>diff OLD-URL[@OLDREV] NEW-URL[@NEWREV]</literal>"
msgstr "<literal>diff OLD-URL[@OLDREV] NEW-URL[@NEWREV]</literal>"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refsect1><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:2005
msgid ""
"Display the differences between two paths.  You can use <command>svn diff</"
"command> in the following ways:"
msgstr ""
"二つのパス間の差分を表示します。<command>svn diff</command>には、以下のような"
"使い方があります。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refsect1><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:2010
msgid ""
"Use just <command>svn diff</command> to display local modifications in a "
"working copy."
msgstr ""
"作業コピーの手元の変更を表示するには、ただ <command>svn diff</command> として"
"ください。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refsect1><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:2015
msgid ""
"Display the changes made to <replaceable>TARGET</replaceable>s as they are "
"seen in <replaceable>REV</replaceable> between two revisions.  "
"<replaceable>TARGET</replaceable>s may be all working copy paths or all "
"<replaceable>URL</replaceable>s.  If <replaceable>TARGET</replaceable>s are "
"working copy paths, <replaceable>N</replaceable> defaults to <literal>BASE</"
"literal> and <replaceable>M</replaceable> to the working copy; if "
"<replaceable>TARGET</replaceable>s are <replaceable>URL</replaceable>s, "
"<replaceable>N</replaceable> must be specified and <replaceable>M</"
"replaceable> defaults to <literal>HEAD</literal>.  The <literal>-c M</"
"literal> option is equivalent to <literal>-r N:M</literal> where <literal>N "
"= M-1</literal>.  Using <literal>-c -M</literal> does the reverse: <literal>-"
"r M:N</literal> where <literal>N = M-1</literal>."
msgstr ""
"<replaceable>REV</replaceable> の二つのリビジョン間に現れる、"
"<replaceable>TARGET</replaceable> にされた変更を表示します。"
"<replaceable>TARGET</replaceable> は、すべて作業コピーパスか、すべて "
"<replaceable>URL</replaceable> です。<replaceable>TARGET</replaceable> が作業"
"コピーパスの場合、<replaceable>N</replaceable> のデフォルト値は "
"<literal>BASE</literal> で、<replaceable>M</replaceable> のデフォルトは作業コ"
"ピーのものです。<replaceable>URL</replaceable> の場合、<replaceable>N</"
"replaceable> は指定せねばならず、<replaceable>M</replaceable> のデフォルト値"
"は <literal>HEAD</literal> です。<literal>-c M</literal> オプションは、"
"<literal>N = M-1</literal> の状態の <literal>-r N:M</literal> と等価です。"
"<literal>-c -M</literal> は逆 (<literal>N = M-1</literal> の状態の <literal>-"
"r M:N</literal>) になります。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refsect1><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:2035
msgid ""
"Display the differences between <replaceable>OLD-TGT</replaceable> as it was "
"seen in <replaceable>OLDREV</replaceable> and <replaceable>NEW-TGT</"
"replaceable> as it was seen in <replaceable>NEWREV</replaceable>.  "
"<replaceable>PATH</replaceable>s, if given, are relative to <replaceable>OLD-"
"TGT</replaceable> and <replaceable>NEW-TGT</replaceable> and restrict the "
"output to differences for those paths.  <replaceable>OLD-TGT</replaceable> "
"and <replaceable>NEW-TGT</replaceable> may be working copy paths or "
"<replaceable>URL[@REV]</replaceable>.  <replaceable>NEW-TGT</replaceable> "
"defaults to <replaceable>OLD-TGT</replaceable> if not specified.  <literal>-"
"r N</literal> makes <replaceable>OLDREV</replaceable> default to <literal>N</"
"literal>; <literal>-r N:M</literal> makes <replaceable>OLDREV</replaceable> "
"default to <replaceable>N</replaceable> and <replaceable>NEWREV</"
"replaceable> default to <replaceable>M</replaceable>."
msgstr ""
"<replaceable>OLDREV</replaceable> にある <replaceable>OLD-TGT</replaceable> "
"と、<replaceable>NEWREV</replaceable> にある <replaceable>NEW-TGT</"
"replaceable> の差分を表示します。<replaceable>PATH</replaceable> を与えた場"
"合、<replaceable>OLD-TGT</replaceable> と <replaceable>NEW-TGT</replaceable> "
"は <replaceable>PATH</replaceable> からの相対パスとなり、差分の出力もそこから"
"に制限されます。<replaceable>OLD-TGT</replaceable> と <replaceable>NEW-TGT</"
"replaceable> は、作業コピーのパスか <replaceable>URL[@REV]</replaceable> にな"
"ります。指定しないと、<replaceable>NEW-TGT</replaceable> のデフォルトは "
"<replaceable>OLD-TGT</replaceable> です。<literal>-r N</literal> とすると "
"<replaceable>OLDREV</replaceable> のデフォルトは <literal>N</literal> にな"
"り、<literal>-r N:M</literal> とすると <replaceable>OLDREV</replaceable> のデ"
"フォルトは <replaceable>N</replaceable> で、<replaceable>NEWREV</"
"replaceable> のデフォルトは <replaceable>M</replaceable> になります。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refsect1><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:2060
msgid ""
"<userinput>svn diff OLD-URL[@OLDREV] NEW-URL[@NEWREV]</userinput> is "
"shorthand for <userinput>svn diff --old=OLD-URL[@OLDREV] --new=NEW-URL"
"[@NEWREV].</userinput>"
msgstr ""
"<userinput>svn diff OLD-URL[@OLDREV] NEW-URL[@NEWREV]</userinput> は "
"<userinput>svn diff --old=OLD-URL[@OLDREV] --new=NEW-URL[@NEWREV].</"
"userinput> の短縮形です。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refsect1><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:2065
msgid ""
"<userinput>svn diff -r N:M URL</userinput> is shorthand for <userinput>svn "
"diff -r N:M --old=URL --new=URL</userinput>."
msgstr ""
"<userinput>svn diff -r N:M URL</userinput> は <userinput>svn diff -r N:M --"
"old=URL --new=URL</userinput> の短縮形です。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refsect1><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:2069
msgid ""
"<userinput>svn diff [-r N[:M]] URL1[@N] URL2[@M]</userinput> is shorthand "
"for <userinput>svn diff [-r N[:M]] --old=URL1 --new=URL2</userinput>."
msgstr ""
"<userinput>svn diff [-r N[:M]] URL1[@N] URL2[@M]</userinput> は "
"<userinput>svn diff [-r N[:M]] --old=URL1 --new=URL2</userinput> の短縮形で"
"す。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refsect1><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:2073
msgid ""
"If <replaceable>TARGET</replaceable> is a URL, then revs <literal>N</"
"literal> and <literal>M</literal> can be given either via the <option>--"
"revision</option> (<option>-r</option>) option or by using the <quote>@</"
"quote> notation as described earlier."
msgstr ""
"<replaceable>TARGET</replaceable> が URL の場合、リビジョン <literal>N</"
"literal> とリビジョン <literal>M</literal> は、<option>--revision</option> "
"(<option>-r</option>) で与えられるか、既に述べたように <quote>@</quote> 記法"
"で指定されたものになります。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refsect1><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:2080
msgid ""
"If <replaceable>TARGET</replaceable> is a working copy path, the default "
"behavior (when no <option>--revision</option> (<option>-r</option>) option "
"is provided) is to display the differences between the base and working "
"copies of <replaceable>TARGET</replaceable>.  If a <option>--revision</"
"option> (<option>-r</option>) option is specified in this scenario, though, "
"it means:"
msgstr ""
"<replaceable>TARGET</replaceable> が作業コピーのパスの場合、デフォルト "
"(<option>--revision</option> (<option>-r</option>) オプションを与えない場合) "
"の振る舞いとして、<replaceable>TARGET</replaceable> のベースと作業コピーの差"
"分を表示します。このシナリオで <option>--revision</option> (<option>-r</"
"option>) オプションを与えた場合、次のような意味になります。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refsect1><variablelist><varlistentry><term>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:2092
msgid "<option>--revision N:M</option>"
msgstr "<option>--revision N:M</option>"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refsect1><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:2094
msgid ""
"The server compares <replaceable>TARGET@N</replaceable> and "
"<replaceable>TARGET@M</replaceable>."
msgstr ""
"サーバーは <replaceable>TARGET@N</replaceable> と <replaceable>TARGET@M</"
"replaceable> を比較します。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refsect1><variablelist><varlistentry><term>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:2100
msgid "<option>--revision N</option>"
msgstr "<option>--revision N</option>"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refsect1><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:2102
msgid ""
"The client compares <replaceable>TARGET@N</replaceable> against the working "
"copy."
msgstr ""
"クライアントは <replaceable>TARGET@N</replaceable> と作業コピーを比較します。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refsect1><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:2110
msgid ""
"If the alternate syntax is used, the server compares <replaceable>URL1</"
"replaceable> and <replaceable>URL2</replaceable> at revisions "
"<replaceable>N</replaceable> and <replaceable>M</replaceable>, "
"respectively.  If either <replaceable>N</replaceable> or <replaceable>M</"
"replaceable> is omitted, a value of <literal>HEAD</literal> is assumed."
msgstr ""
"別の構文を使うと、サーバはそれぞれリビジョン <replaceable>N</replaceable> と "
"<replaceable>M</replaceable> にある <replaceable>URL1</replaceable> と "
"<replaceable>URL2</replaceable> を比較します。もし <replaceable>N</"
"replaceable> や <replaceable>M</replaceable> が省略されれば、 <literal>HEAD</"
"literal> の値が使われます。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refsect1><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:2119
msgid ""
"By default, <command>svn diff</command> ignores the ancestry of files and "
"merely compares the contents of the two files being compared.  If you use "
"<option>--notice-ancestry</option>, the ancestry of the paths in question "
"will be taken into consideration when comparing revisions (i.e., if you run "
"<command>svn diff</command> on two files with identical contents but "
"different ancestry, you will see the entire contents of the file as having "
"been removed and added again)."
msgstr ""
"デフォルトでは、<command>svn diff</command> はファイルの系統を無視し、単に比"
"較対象になっている二つのファイルの内容を比較するだけです。<option>--notice-"
"ancestry</option> を使うとリビジョンを比較する際に、問題になっているパスの系"
"統が考慮されます (つまり、同じ内容を持ってはいるが異なる系統を持つ、二つの"
"ファイルに対して <command>svn diff</command> を実行すると、ファイル全体が一度"
"削除され、もう一度すべてが追加されたような結果を得ることになります)。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refsect1><informalexample><screen>
