#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refsect1><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:3119
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The <option>--verbose</option> (<option>-v</option>)  option causes "
"<command>svn log</command> to include information about the paths that were "
"changed in each displayed revision.  These paths appear, one path per line "
"of output, with action codes that indicate what type of change was made to "
"the path."
msgstr ""
"<option>--verbose</option> オプションを使用すると、それぞれの表示したリビジョ"
"ンで変更した、パスの情報を <command>svn log</command> に含めるようになりま"
"す。表示したパスには、1 行づつ、そのパスにどのような変更を加えたかを表すアク"
"ションコードが付きます。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refsect1><informalexample><screen>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:3128
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"$ svn log -v http://svn.red-bean.com/repos/test/ foo.c bar.c\n"
