"&lt;/logentry&gt;\n"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refsect1><tip><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:3267
msgid ""
"Sometimes when you run <command>svn log</command> on a specific path and a "
"specific revision, you see no log information output at all, as in the "
"following:"
msgstr ""
"<command>svn log</command> を特定のパスの特定のリビジョンを指定して実行したの"
"に、以下のように何も表示しない場合があります。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refsect1><tip><informalexample><screen>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:3273
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"$ svn log -r 20 http://svn.red-bean.com/untouched.txt\n"
"------------------------------------------------------------------------\n"
msgstr ""
"$ svn log -r 20 http://svn.red-bean.com/untouched.txt\n"
"------------------------------------------------------------------------\n"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refsect1><tip><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:3278
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"That just means the path wasn't modified in that revision.  To get log "
"information for that revision, either run the log operation against the "
"repository's root URL, or specify a path that you happen to know was changed "
"in that revision:"
msgstr ""
"これは、そのパスはそのリビジョンで修正されなかったことを意味しています。その"
"リビジョンのログ情報を取得するには、リポジトリーのルート URL で log するか、"
"そのリビジョンで修正したファイルを知っている場合、明示的にそれを指定してくだ"
"さい。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refsect1><tip><informalexample><screen>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:3286
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"$ svn log -r 20 touched.txt \n"
"------------------------------------------------------------------------\n"
"r20 | sally | 2003-01-17 22:56:19 -0600 (Fri, 17 Jan 2003) | 1 line\n"
"\n"
"Made a change.\n"
"------------------------------------------------------------------------\n"
msgstr ""
"$ svn log -r 20 touched.txt \n"
"------------------------------------------------------------------------\n"
"r20 | sally | 2003-01-17 22:56:19 +0900 (金, 17 1月 2003) | 1 line\n"
"\n"
"Made a change.\n"
"------------------------------------------------------------------------\n"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refsect1><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:3296
msgid ""
"Beginning with Subversion 1.7, users can take advantage of a special output "
"mode which combines the information from <command>svn log</command> with "
"what you would see when running <command>svn diff</command> on the same "
"targets for each revision of the log.  Simply invoke <command>svn log</"
"command> with the <option>--diff</option> option to trigger this output mode."
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refsect1><informalexample><screen>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:3307
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"$ svn log -r 20 touched.txt --diff\n"
"------------------------------------------------------------------------\n"
"r20 | sally | 2003-01-17 22:56:19 -0600 (Fri, 17 Jan 2003) | 1 line\n"
"\n"
"Made a change.\n"
"\n"
"Index: touched.txt\n"
"===================================================================\n"
"--- touched.txt\t(revision 19)\n"
"+++ touched.txt\t(revision 20)\n"
"@@ -1 +1,2 @@\n"
" This is the file 'touched.txt'.\n"
"+We add such exciting text to files around here!\n"
"------------------------------------------------------------------------\n"
"$\n"
msgstr ""
"$ svn log -r 20 touched.txt --diff\n"
"------------------------------------------------------------------------\n"
"r20 | sally | 2003-01-17 22:56:19 -0600 (金, 17 1月 2003) | 1 line\n"
"\n"
"Made a change.\n"
"\n"
"Index: touched.txt\n"
"===================================================================\n"
"--- touched.txt\t(revision 19)\n"
"+++ touched.txt\t(revision 20)\n"
"@@ -1 +1,2 @@\n"
" This is the file 'touched.txt'.\n"
"+We add such exciting text to files around here!\n"
"------------------------------------------------------------------------\n"
"$\n"

