"$ svn propset svn:executable ON somescript\n"
"property 'svn:executable' set on 'somescript'\n"
msgstr ""
"$ svn propset svn:executable ON somescript\n"
"属性 'svn:executable' を 'somescript' に設定しました\n"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refsect1><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:4462
msgid ""
"Perhaps you have an internal policy to set certain properties for the "
"benefit of your coworkers:"
