"specified by the <option>--accept</option> argument and then removes "
"conflict-related artifact files.  This allows <replaceable>PATH</"
"replaceable> to be committed again&mdash;that is, it tells Subversion that "
"the conflicts have been <quote>resolved.</quote>.  You can pass the "
"following arguments to the <option>--accept</option> command depending on "
"your desired resolution:"
msgstr ""
"作業コピーのファイルやディレクトリの <quote>競合</quote> 状態を解決します。こ"
