"See <xref linkend=\"svn.tour.cycle.resolve\"/> for an in-depth look at "
"resolving conflicts."
msgstr ""
"競合解決について深く掘り下げた話題は <xref linkend=\"svn.tour.cycle.resolve"
"\"/> をご覧ください。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refsect1><informalexample><screen>
