"<filename>stderr</filename>.  Dump revisions <replaceable>LOWER</"
"replaceable> rev through <replaceable>UPPER</replaceable> rev.  If no "
"revisions are given, dump all revision trees.  If only <replaceable>LOWER</"
"replaceable> is given, dump that one revision tree.  See <xref linkend=\"svn."
"reposadmin.maint.migrate\"/> for a practical use."
msgstr ""
