#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:7036
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Recovering the database requires an exclusive lock on the repository. (This "
"is a <quote>database lock</quote>; see the sidebar <xref linkend=\"svn."
"advanced.locking.meanings\"/>.)  If another process is accessing the "
