"&hellip;\n"
msgstr ""
"$ svnlook cat -t ax8 /var/svn/repos /trunk/README\n"
"\n"
"               Subversion, a version control system.\n"
"               =====================================\n"
"\n"
"$LastChangedDate: 2003-07-17 10:45:25 -0500 (Thu, 17 Jul 2003) $\n"
"\n"
"Contents:\n"
"\n"
"     I. A FEW POINTERS\n"
