"$ svnlook changed -r 64 /var/svn/repos\n"
"A   trunk/vendors/baker/toast.txt\n"
"D   trunk/vendors/baker/bread.txt\n"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><sect2><refentry><refsect1><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:7848
msgid ""
"Unfortunately, nothing in the preceding output reveals the connection "
"between the deleted and added files.  Use the <option>--copy-info</option> "
"option to make this relationship more apparent:"
