#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><title>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:10283
msgid "svnversion&mdash;Subversion Working Copy Version Info"
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><refentry><refnamediv><refpurpose>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:10294
msgid "Summarize the local revision(s) of a working copy."
msgstr "作業コピーにある、ローカルリビジョンについてのまとめを表示します。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><refentry><refsect1><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:10300
msgid "<literal>svnversion [OPTIONS] [WC_PATH [TRAIL_URL]]</literal>"
msgstr "<literal>svnversion [OPTIONS] [WC_PATH [TRAIL_URL]]</literal>"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><refentry><refsect1><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:10306
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"<command>svnversion</command> is a program for summarizing the revision "
"mixture of a working copy.  The resultant revision number, or revision "
"range, is written to standard output."
msgstr ""
"<command>svnversion</command> は、作業コピーの混合リビジョン状況を表示するプ"
"ログラムです。リビジョン番号またはリビジョン範囲を標準出力に書き出します。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><refentry><refsect1><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:10311
msgid ""
"It's common to use this output in your build process when defining the "
"version number of your program."
msgstr ""
"ビルドプロセス中で、プログラムのバージョン番号を定義する際、この出力を使用す"
"るのが一般的です。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><refentry><refsect1><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:10314
msgid ""
"<replaceable>TRAIL_URL</replaceable>, if present, is the trailing portion of "
"the URL used to determine whether <replaceable>WC_PATH</replaceable> itself "
"is switched (detection of switches within <replaceable>WC_PATH</replaceable> "
"does not rely on <replaceable>TRAIL_URL</replaceable>)."
msgstr ""
"<replaceable>TRAIL_URL</replaceable> を指定した場合、<replaceable>TRAIL_URL</"
"replaceable> を <replaceable>WC_PATH</replaceable> が切り替わったかどうかを決"
"める、URL の末尾として利用します (<replaceable>WC_PATH</replaceable> 内部での"
"切り替えは <replaceable>TRAIL_URL</replaceable> を利用しません)。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><refentry><refsect1><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:10321
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"When <replaceable>WC_PATH</replaceable> is not defined, the current "
"directory will be used as the working copy path.  <replaceable>TRAIL_URL</"
"replaceable> cannot be defined if <replaceable>WC_PATH</replaceable> is not "
"explicitly given."
msgstr ""
"<replaceable>WC_PATH</replaceable> を定義していない場合、作業コピーのパスとし"
"てカレントディレクトリを使用します。<replaceable>WC_PATH</replaceable> を明示"
"的に与えておかないと、<replaceable>TRAIL_URL</replaceable> を定義できません。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><refentry><refsect1><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:10332
msgid ""
"Like <command>svnserve</command>, <command>svnversion</command> has no "
"subcommands&mdash;only options:"
msgstr ""
"<command>svnserve</command> と同様に、<command>svnversion</command> にサブコ"
"マンドはありません。オプションがあるだけです。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><refentry><refsect1><variablelist><varlistentry><term>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:10339
msgid "<option>--no-newline</option> (<option>-n</option>)"
msgstr "<option>--no-newline</option> (<option>-n</option>)"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><refentry><refsect1><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:10341
msgid "Omits the usual trailing newline from the output."
msgstr "出力の末尾にある、通常の改行文字を省略します。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><refentry><refsect1><variablelist><varlistentry><term>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:10346
msgid "<option>--committed</option> (<option>-c</option>)"
msgstr "<option>--committed</option> (<option>-c</option>)"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><refentry><refsect1><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:10348
msgid ""
"Uses the last-changed revisions rather than the current (i.e., highest "
"locally available) revisions."
msgstr ""
"現在の (つまりローカルで一番新しい) リビジョンではなく、最終更新リビジョンを"
"使用します。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><refentry><refsect1><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:10356
msgid "Prints a help summary."
msgstr "ヘルプの概要を出力します。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><refentry><refsect1><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:10363
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Requests that the client print only essential information while "
#| "performing an operation."
msgid ""
"Requests that the program print only essential information while performing "
"an operation."
msgstr "実行中に重要な情報だけを出力するように指示します。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><refentry><refsect1><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:10371
msgid ""
"Prints the version of <command>svnversion</command> and exit with no error."
msgstr "<command>svnversion</command> のバージョンを出力して正常終了します。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><refentry><refsect1><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:10382
msgid ""
"If the working copy is all at the same revision (e.g., immediately after an "
"update), then that revision is printed out:"
msgstr ""
"作業コピーが完全に同一リビジョンである場合 (たとえば update の直後など)、リビ"
"ジョンを以下のように出力します。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><refentry><refsect1><informalexample><screen>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:10388
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"$ svnversion\n"
"4168\n"
msgstr ""
"$ svnversion\n"
"4168\n"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><refentry><refsect1><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:10393
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"You can add <replaceable>TRAIL_URL</replaceable> to make sure the working "
"copy is not switched from what you expect.  Note that the "
"<replaceable>WC_PATH</replaceable> is required in this command:"
msgstr ""
"想定する作業コピーから切り替わっていないことを保証するため、"
"<replaceable>TRAIL_URL</replaceable> を追加できます。このコマンドには "
"<replaceable>WC_PATH</replaceable> が必要なことに注意してください。"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><refentry><refsect1><informalexample><screen>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:10400
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"$ svnversion . /var/svn/trunk\n"
"4168\n"
