"の、掘り下げた説明は<xref linkend=\"svn.serverconfig.pathbasedauthz\"/> をご"
"覧ください、"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><sect1><refentry><refsect1><para>
#: en/book/ch09-reference.xml:10844
msgid ""
"These are the <filename>httpd.conf</filename> directives that apply to "
"<command>mod_authz_svn</command>:"
msgstr ""
"以下は、<command>mod_authz_svn</command> に適用する <filename>httpd.conf</"
